%5B%7B%22title%22%3A%22I%20spent%20a%20night%20in%20Panama's%20richest%20neighborhood%2C%20often%20called%20a%20'little%20Dubai'%20or%20the%20'Miami%20of%20Latin%20America'%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222048%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20Punta%20Pacifica%20neighborhood%20in%20Panama%20City.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F663bc52bf27898f532d5292a%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221536%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20author%20in%20the%20pool%20at%20the%20JW%20Marriott%20Panama.%3Cp%3EMonica%20Humphries%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EPunta%20Pacifica%20is%20Panama%20City's%20most%20expensive%20neighborhood.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20neighborhood%20has%20man-made%20islands%2C%20private%20marinas%2C%20and%20penthouses%20worth%20%245%20million.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EI%20stayed%20at%20the%20five-star%20JW%20Marriott%20Panama%20and%20experienced%20the%20neighborhood's%20luxury%20firsthand.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EDuncan%20McGowan%20describes%20Panama%20City's%20Ocean%20Reef%20Islands%20as%20%26quot%3Bperfection.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20landscaping%20is%20manicured%20flawlessly%2C%20never%20a%20leaf%20or%20branch%20out%20of%20place.%20You'd%20have%20to%20hunt%20to%20find%20trash%20anywhere%20on%20the%20islands%2C%20and%20instead%2C%20you're%20more%20likely%20to%20notice%20bird%20songs%20filling%20the%20air.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELooking%20one%20way%2C%20all%20you%20see%20is%20the%20endless%20ocean.%20Turn%20around%2C%20and%20there's%20a%20stunning%20cityscape%20behind%20you%2C%20McGowan%2C%20the%20president%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.puntapacificarealty.com%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EPunta%20Pacifica%20Realty%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20told%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Ocean%20Reef%20Islands%20are%20part%20of%20Panama's%20Punta%20Pacifica%20neighborhood%2C%20and%20that%20perfection%20is%20exactly%20what%20Panama's%20wealthiest%20residents%20seek.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20a%20recent%20trip%20to%20the%20country%2C%20I%20saw%20the%20opulence%20that%20residents%20chase%20across%20Punta%20Pacifica%2C%20Panama's%20wealthiest%20neighborhood.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EI%20landed%20in%20Panama%20City%2C%20snapped%20skyline%20pictures%2C%20and%20texted%20my%20friends%20that%20I%20had%20arrived.%20Immediately%2C%20one%20pointed%20out%20how%20the%20city%20resembled%20Miami.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222048%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Panama's%20Punta%20Pacifica%20skyline.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F663d0dd89686a6f37bfde5b7%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221365%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EPanama's%20Punta%20Pacifica%20skyline.%3Cp%3EMonica%20Humphries%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EI%20spent%20my%20first%20night%20in%20Casco%20Viejo%2C%20Panama%20City's%20old%20town.%20From%20the%20coast%2C%20I%20could%20look%20out%20onto%20Punta%20Pacifica%2C%20where%20a%20grouping%20of%20tall%20buildings%20reached%20out%20to%20the%20clouds.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20friend's%20initial%20thoughts%20about%20Punta%20Pacifica%20aren't%20uncommon.%20McGowan%20said%20people%20always%20compare%20Punta%20Pacifica%20to%20dense%20cities%20like%20Miami%2C%20New%20York%20City%2C%20and%20Dubai.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.centralamerica.com%2Fexperiencing%2Ftravel%2Fpunta-pacifica-panama-city%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ECentral%20America%20Living%3C%2Fa%3E%20refers%20to%20the%20neighborhood%20as%20a%20%26quot%3Bmini-Dubai%2C%26quot%3B%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nytimes.com%2F2014%2F04%2F04%2Fgreathomesanddestinations%2Fpanama-seizes-on-glimmers-of-real-estate-resurgence.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EThe%20New%20York%20Times%3C%2Fa%3E%20said%20in%202014%20that%20Punta%20Pacifica%20is%20%26quot%3Boften%20called%20the%20Miami%20of%20Latin%20America.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20comparisons%20made%20sense.%20All%20three%20cities%20are%20home%20to%20impressive%20skyscrapers%20and%20coastlines.%20And%20since%20Punta%20Pacifica%20is%20home%20to%20the%20Ocean%20Reef%20Islands%2C%20which%20were%20man-made%20in%20the%20early%202000s%2C%20it's%20easy%20to%20see%20how%20it's%20grouped%20with%20Dubai.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20McGowan%20said%20that%20they%20are%20vastly%20different%20destinations.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20resembles%20all%20of%20them%2C%20but%20it%20has%20its%20own%20flavor%2C%26quot%3B%20McGowan%20said.%20%26quot%3BI%20think%20Panama%20City%20and%20Punta%20Pacifica%20have%20matured%20enough%20now%20that%20it%20doesn't%20have%20to%20be%20compared.%20It%20stands%20on%20its%20own.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EThe%20next%20day%2C%20I%20headed%20to%20Punta%20Pacifica.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222048%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20Punta%20Pacifica%20neighborhood%20in%20Panama%20City.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F663bc529b4abc992e8c70655%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221536%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ECondo%20and%20apartment%20buildings%20in%20Punta%20Pacifica%2C%20Panama.%20%3Cp%3EMonica%20Humphries%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThree%20decades%20ago%2C%20Punta%20Pacifica%20didn't%20exist.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECreated%20in%20the%20early%202000s%2C%20a%20company%20that%20built%20one%20of%20Panama%20City's%20major%20highways%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ciel.org%2FPublications%2FIFCCSPanama.pdf%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eearned%20the%20rights%20to%20develop%3C%2Fa%3E%2086%20acres%20of%20landfill%20and%2073%20acres%20of%20mainland%20along%20an%20area%20of%20the%20city's%20coast%20known%20today%20as%20Punta%20Pacifica.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMcGowan%2C%20who%20has%20worked%20in%20Panama's%20real-estate%20market%20for%20nearly%20two%20decades%2C%20said%20it%20was%20designed%20as%20a%20luxury%20area%20from%20the%20start%2C%20and%20living%20in%20Punta%20Pacifica%20can%20come%20at%20a%20steep%20price.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20neighborhood%20is%20home%20to%20more%20than%20a%20dozen%20condominiums%20and%20apartment%20complexes%2C%20which%20can%20range%20in%20price.%20On%20the%20lower%20end%2C%20McGowan%20said%20residents%20can%20expect%20to%20pay%20around%20%242%2C200%20a%20square%20meter%2C%20while%20prime%20real%20estate%20can%20cost%20%247%2C000%20a%20square%20meter.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20quick%20search%20on%20Punta%20Pacifica%20Realty%20or%20Panama%20Realtor%20shows%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.panamarealtor.com%2Fproperty%2F40731%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eone-bedroom%20apartments%20for%20sale%20at%20%24200%2C000%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.panamarealtor.com%2Fproperty%2F32694%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eluxury%20penthouses%20for%20as%20much%20as%20%245%20million%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EI%20spent%20a%20night%20in%20the%20neighborhood's%20famous%20TOC%20building.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222048%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20Punta%20Pacifica%20neighborhood%20in%20Panama%20City.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F663bc529b4abc992e8c70656%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221536%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20TOC%20building%20in%20Panama's%20Punta%20Pacifica%20Neighborhood.%20%3Cp%3EMonica%20Humphries%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20building%20stands%20out%20in%20Punta%20Pacifica's%20skyline%20with%20its%20sail-like%20shape%3A%20the%20TOC%20building.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EToday%2C%20TOC%20stands%20for%20The%20Ocean%20Club%2C%20but%20ask%20anyone%20in%20Panama%2C%20and%20they%20know%20it%20by%20its%20former%20name%2C%20the%20Trump%20Ocean%20Club.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Trump%20Organization%20wasn't%20the%20building%20developer%3B%20local%20developer%20Roger%20Khafif%20was.%20However%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.usnews.com%2Fnews%2Fpolitics%2Farticles%2F2015%2F10%2F12%2Fap-exclusive-panama-condo-owners-to-trump-youre-fired%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ethe%20Associated%20Press%20reported%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20the%20Trump%20name%20was%20licensed%20to%20the%20building%20to%20increase%20its%20credibility%20and%20notoriety.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20became%20Ivanka%20Trump's%20business%20project%20in%202006%2C%20according%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nbcnews.com%2Fnews%2Finvestigations%2Fpanama-tower-carries-trump-s-name-ties-organized-crime-n821706%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ENBC%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20since%20its%20opening%20in%202011%2C%20the%20building's%20history%20has%20been%20riddled%20with%20scandals.%20An%20NBC%20and%20Reuters%20investigation%20found%20that%20many%20of%20the%20property's%20brokers%2C%20customers%2C%20and%20investors%20were%20tied%20to%20drug%20trafficking%20and%20international%20crime.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%202015%2C%20the%20AP%20reported%20that%20%26quot%3Bconcerns%20about%20overspending%20and%20transparency%26quot%3B%20led%20the%20Trump%20management%20company%20to%20be%20forced%20out%20after%20a%20vote%20by%20condo%20owners%20and%20board%20members.%20However%2C%20the%20Trump%20Organization%20refused%20to%20accept%20the%20vote%20and%20claimed%20that%20it%20quit%20instead.%20Along%20with%20that%20announcement%2C%20the%20Trump%20Organization%20demanded%20a%20%245%20million%20termination%20fee%2C%20according%20to%20the%20outlet.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%202018%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.seattletimes.com%2Fnation-world%2Fformer-trump-hotel-in-panama-city-rebranded-as-jw-marriott%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ethe%20AP%20reported%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20Marriott%20International%20took%20over%20management%20and%20renamed%20it%20The%20Ocean%20Club%20to%20keep%20its%20TOC%20branding.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EToday%2C%20the%2070-story%20building%20is%20one%20of%20the%20largest%20mixed-use%20buildings%20in%20Panama.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5