venka%20has%20been%20looking%20after%20her%20skin%20since%20her%20early%20teens%2C%20following%20a%20skincare%20regimen%20every%20morning%20and%20night%2C%20never%20going%20to%20bed%20with%20makeup%20on%2C%20and%20using%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdermatologist-anti-aging-skincare-routine-products-2023-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eantiaging%20products%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2252cde51b-e708-46ba-a9fa-ee8a53d3ed8b%5C%22%3ESunscreen%20is%20the%20most%20important%20part%20of%20Nevenka's%20routine%2C%20a%20dermatologist%20says%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EDr.%20Derek%20V.%20Chan%2C%20a%20board-certified%20medical%20and%20cosmetic%20dermatologist%20in%20Manhattan%2C%20told%20BI%20that%20wearing%20sunscreen%20is%20%26quot%3Bby%20far%20the%20most%20important%20part%26quot%3B%20of%20Nevenka's%20skincare%20routine.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20Nevenka%20is%20outside%2C%20she%20always%20wears%20sunglasses%2C%20a%20hat%2C%20and%20sunscreen%2C%20Palmyra%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EChan%20recommended%20wearing%20sunscreen%20with%20an%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fbeauty%2Fspf-meaning%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ESPF%20factor%20of%20at%20least%2030%3C%2Fa%3E%20every%20day%2C%20and%20wearing%20a%20broad-brimmed%20hat%2C%20which%20is%20more%20protective%20than%20a%20baseball%20cap.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22fd98b6b6-eb5a-4f06-9915-968570886e7a%5C%22%3EShe%20uses%20lots%20of%20hydrating%2C%20antiaging%20skincare%20products%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ENevenka%20has%20been%20using%20the%20following%20products%20for%20over%2050%20years%2C%20Palmyra%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EClarins%20Velvet%20Cleansing%20Milk%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20%E2%80%94%20Nevenka%20applies%20this%20cleanser%20and%20removes%20it%20with%20cotton%20rounds.%20Chan%20said%20this%20product%20helps%20to%20maintain%20and%20rebuild%20the%20skin%20barrier%2C%20so%20it%20aids%20skin%20hydration.%20It%20has%20antiaging%20properties%20too%2C%20because%20it%20contains%20yellow%20gentian%2C%20which%20protects%20against%20ultraviolet-induced%20DNA%20damage%2C%20and%20moringa%20oil%2C%20which%20can%20help%20reduce%20fine%20lines%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EClarins%20Hydrating%20Toning%20Lotion%20%3C%2Fstrong%3E%E2%80%94%20This%20lotion%20contains%20aloe%20vera%2C%20which%20can%20protect%20against%20ultraviolet%20damage%20and%20help%20prevent%20photo-aging%2C%20Chan%20said.%20Plus%2C%20the%20fig%20tree%20and%20crocus%20in%20it%20help%20even%20out%20skin%20tone.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ELanc%C3%B4me%20Genifique%20Serum%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20%E2%80%94%20Like%20the%20Clarins%20Cleansing%20Milk%2C%20this%20serum%20contains%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fbeauty%2Fvitamin-c-for-skin%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Evitamin%20C%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20which%20has%20antiaging%20properties%20because%20it%20helps%20decrease%20hyperpigmentation%20and%20increases%20the%20production%20of%20collagen%2C%20which%20helps%20lessen%20the%20appearance%20of%20fine%20lines%2C%20Chan%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EElizabeth%20Arden%20Ceramide%20Lift%20%26amp%3B%20Firm%20Night%20Cream%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20%E2%80%94%20Chan%20said%20that%20this%20product%20contains%20ceramides%2C%20which%20he%20likes%20because%20they%20help%20rebuild%20the%20skin%20barrier%20and%20help%20the%20skin%20stay%20hydrated.%20Because%20the%20skin%20produces%20fewer%20ceramides%20as%20it%20ages%2C%20they%20can%20have%20an%20antiaging%20effect%20when%20applied.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20night%20cream%20also%20contains%20edelweiss%20extract%2C%20which%20has%20%26quot%3Bmultiple%20antiaging%20effects%2C%26quot%3B%20Chan%20said%2C%20including%20improving%20eye%20wrinkles%20and%20skin%20density%2C%20elasticity%2C%20and%20thickness.%20Nevenka%20applies%20this%20on%20her%20face%20and%20decolletage.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ELanc%C3%B4me%20Teint%20Idol%20foundation%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20%E2%80%94%20This