024%2Ffilm%2Fglobal%2Fnasty-ilie-nastase-cannes-1236008608%2Famp%2F%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2F2024%2Ffilm%2Fglobal%2Fnasty-ilie-nastase-cannes-1236008608%2Famp%2F%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BOperation%20Jhaadu%26quot%3B%3A%20Arvind%20Kejriwal%20Claims%20BJP%20Trying%20To%20%26quot%3BFinish%26quot%3B%20AAP%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EDelhi%20Chief%20Minister%20Arvind%20Kejriwal%2C%20accompanied%20by%20senior%20leaders%20of%20the%20Aam%20Aadmi%20Party%20(AAP)%2C%20ahead%20of%20a%20planned%20march%20to%20the%20BJP%20headquarters%20today%20declared%20that%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20can%20send%20anyone%20he%20wishes%20to%20jail.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Kejriwal%20alleged%20that%20the%20BJP%20sees%20AAP%20as%20a%20threat%2C%20prompting%20what%20he%20terms%20%26quot%3BOperation%20Jhaadu%26quot%3B%20-%20a%20concerted%20campaign%20to%20undermine%20his%20party.%20%26quot%3BThe%20PM%20has%20made%20up%20his%20mind%20to%20crush%20the%20Aam%20Aadmi%20Party%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Kejriwal%20said%2C%20claiming%20that%20the%20operation%20involves%20arresting%20prominent%20AAP%20leaders%2C%20seizing%20the%20party's%20bank%20accounts%2C%20and%20shutting%20down%20their%20offices.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThey%20have%20an%20'Operation%20Jhaadu'%20ongoing%2C%20which%20is%20that%20ever%20since%20I%20got%20bail%2C%20the%20PM%20has%20not%20stopped%20talking%20about%20AAP%2C%20that%20AAP%20is%20working%20well%20and%20the%20whole%20country%20is%20talking%20about%20their%20work%20and%20this%20party%20poses%20a%20threat%20to%20the%20BJP%2C%20which%20is%20why%20it%20is%20imperative%20to%20tackle%20with%20this%20party%20now%20itself%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Kejriwal%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20video%20message%20yesterday%2C%20Mr%20Kejriwal%20announced%20his%20intention%20to%20march%20to%20the%20BJP%20headquarters%20alongside%20all%20senior%20AAP%20leaders.%20However%2C%20the%20police%20stated%20that%20AAP%20had%20not%20requested%20permission%20for%20any%20march%20and%20would%20not%20be%20permitted%20to%20hold%20a%20protest%20outside%20their%20premises.%20Additionally%2C%20in%20a%20traffic%20advisory%2C%20the%20police%20advised%20commuters%20to%20avoid%20DDU%20Marg%2C%20IP%20Marg%2C%20Minto%20Road%2C%20and%20Vikas%20Marg.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDespite%20Delhi%20Police's%20statement%2C%20Mr%20Kejriwal%20and%20his%20top%20AAP%20leaders%20are%20currently%20marching%20towards%20the%20BJP%20headquarters.%C2%A0Several%20AAP%20workers%20were%20detained%20as%20they%20attempted%20to%20march%20towards%20the%20BJP%20office.%C2%A0DCP%20Delhi%20Central%2C%20Harsha%20Vardhan%20Mandava%2C%20said%20that%20Section%20144%20had%20been%20imposed%20on%20DDU%20Marg%2C%20prohibiting%20any%20form%20of%20protest.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20recent%20arrest%20of%20Mr%20Kejriwal's%20aide%2C%20Bibhav%20Kumar%2C%20linked%20to%20an%20alleged%20assault%20on%20AAP%20MP%20Swati%20Maliwal%20has%20heightened%20tensions%20between%20AAP%20and%20the%20BJP.%20Mr%20Kejriwal%20alleges%20that%20further%20arrests%20are%20planned%2C%20including%20those%20of%20another%20AAP%20MP%20Raghav%20Chadha%20and%20Delhi%20ministers%20Atishi%20and%20Saurabh%20Bharadwaj.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBJP%20thinks%20that%20this%20way%20they%20can%20do%20away%20with%20us.%20No.%20That%20cannot%20happen%2C%20this%20is%20not%20a%20party%20but%20a%20force%20of%20140%20crore%20people%20who%20have%20done%20immense%20work%20in%20Punjab%2C%20Delhi%20and%20across%20the%20country%20that%20people%20must%20not%20have%20seen%20in%20the%20past%2075%20years%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Delhi%20Chief%20Minister%20accused%C2%A0%20PM%20Modi%20of%20systematically%20targeting%20AAP%20leaders%20like%20Manish%20Sisodia%2C%20Satyendar%20Jain%2C%20and%20Sanjay%20Singh%20by%20sending%20them%20to%20jail%20on%20various%20charges.%20%26quot%3BYou%20think%20that%20you%20will%20crush%20the%20Aam%20Aadmi%20Party%20by%20putting%20its%20leaders%20in%20jail%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Kejriwal%20challenged.%20%26quot%3BThe%20AAP%20is%20not%20going%20to%20be%20crushed%20like%20this.%20You%20try%20it%20once%20and%20see.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20have%20provided%20free%20electricity%20and%20water%2C%20we%20have%20saved%20money%20with%20honesty%20and%20made%20electricity%20free.%20These%20things%20BJP%20has%20never%20done%20and%20cannot%20do%20as%20they%20are%20dishonest%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Kejriwal%20claimed.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Kejriwal%2C%20who%20was%20arrested%20in%20connection%20with%20a%20money%20laundering%20case%20related%20to%20the%20Delhi%20excise%20policy%20scam%2C%20has%20been%20granted%20interim%20bail%20by%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20until%20June%201%2C%20allowing%20him%20to%20campaign%20for%20the%20upcoming%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections.%20However%2C%20he%20is%20required%20to%20surrender%20and%20return%20to%20jail%20on%20June%202%2C%20just%20after%20the%20final%20phase%20of%20polling.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20AAP's%20achievements%20in%20governance%2C%20Mr%20Kejriwal%20stated%2C%20%26quot%3BWe%20have%20worked%20on%20schools%2C%20clinics%3B%20everywhere%20we%20have%20fostered%20a%20good%20spirit%20and%20thought.%20You%20cannot%20bring%20down%20such%20ideology.%20You%20cannot%20trap%20or%20stop%20such%20ideology.%20It%20is%20spreading%20across%20the%20nation.%20You%20arrest%20one%20Kejriwal%20and%201%2C000%20Kejriwals%20will%20be%20born%20in%20this%20country.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Delhi%20Chief%20Minister%20also%20addressed%20various%20allegations%20made%20by%20the%20BJP%20in%20connection%20with%20the%20alleged%20liquor%20policy%20scam.%20%26quot%3BIf%20there%20was%20a%20liquor%20scam%2C%20then%20where%20is%20the%20money%20seized%3F%20Even%20in%20the%20Supreme%20Court%2C%20they%20said%20they%20have%20not%20been%20able%20to%20recover%20anything.%20How%20is%20it%20possible%20that%20if%20it%20is%20a%20scam%20of%20crores%2C%20you%20have%20not%20recovered%20even%20Rs%201%2C000%3F%26quot%3B%20he%20questioned.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20further%20criticised%20Prime%20Minister%20Modi%20for%20labelling%20him%20a%20%26quot%3BKhalistani%20politician%26quot%3B%20during%20a%20rally%2C%20describing%20such%20tactics%20as%20shameful%20and%20indicative%20of%20the%20lengths%20the%20BJP%20will%20go%20to%20malign%20its%20opponents.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BPM%20Modi%20said%20at%20a%20rally%20that%20Kejriwal%20is%20a%20Khalistani%20politician%2C%20if%20this%20is%20what%20a%20PM%20has%20to%20say%20to%20woo%20voters%20then%20it%20is%20shameful.%20Just%20see%20how%20many%20more%20made-up%20stories%20PM%20Modi%20will%20brew%20now.%20BJP%20will%20go%20to%20any%20ends%20and%20will%20stoop%20lower%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Kejriwal%20claimed.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1716105960000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-04%2F4017k9qo_arvind-kejriwal-in-assam_625x300_02_April_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Foperation-jhaadu-arvind-kejriwal-claims-bjp-trying-to-finish-aap-5696635%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Delhi%20Chief%20Minister%20Arvind%20Kejriwal%2C%20accompanied%20by%20senior%20leaders%20of%20the%20Aam%20Aadmi%20Party%20(AAP)%2C%20ahead%20of%20a%20planned%20march%20to%20the%20BJP%20headquarters%20today%20declared%20that%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20can%20send%20anyone%20he%20wishes%20to%20jail.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Foperation-jhaadu-arvind-kejriwal-claims-bjp-trying-to-finish-aap-5696635%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Foperation-jhaadu-arvind-kejriwal-claims-bjp-trying-to-finish-aap-5696635%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Foperation-jhaadu-arvind-kejriwal-claims-bjp-trying-to-finish-aap-5696635%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Selena%20Gomez%2C%20Zoe%20Salda%C3%B1a%20