n%3Cp%3EWhen%20the%20India%20Against%20Corruption%20movement%20catapulted%20Mr%20Kejriwal%20to%20national%20limelight%2C%20Bibhav%20Kumar%20was%20with%20him.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20AAP%20swept%20the%202015%20election%20in%20Delhi%2C%20Bibhav%20Kumar%20was%20appointed%20Mr%20Kejriwal's%20private%20secretary.%20He%20was%20reappointed%20in%202020%20when%20AAP%20returned%20to%20power%20in%20the%20national%20capital.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKnown%20to%20work%20behind%20the%20scenes%2C%20Bibhav%20Kumar's%20influence%20was%20such%20that%20anyone%2C%20be%20it%20mediapersons%20or%20AAP%20functionaries%2C%20had%20to%20go%20through%20him%20if%20he%2Fshe%20wanted%20to%20meet%20Mr%20Kejriwal.%20He%20is%20among%20Mr%20Kejriwal's%20most%20trusted%20aides%20and%20is%20known%20to%20play%20a%20key%20role%20in%20shaping%20AAP's%20strategies.%C2%A0%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20'shadow'%20first%20came%20under%20the%20spotlight%20last%20year%20when%20Delhi's%20directorate%20of%20vigilance%20questioned%20why%20he%20had%20been%20allotted%20a%20Type%20VI%20bungalow%20in%20violation%20of%20rules.%20Soon%20after%2C%20the%20Public%20Works%20Department%20cancelled%20the%20allotment.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20February%20this%20year%2C%20he%20was%20questioned%20by%20the%20Enforcement%20Directorate%20in%20connection%20with%20alleged%20irregularities%20in%20Delhi's%20now-scrapped%20liquor%20policy%20that%20led%20to%20the%20arrest%20of%20top%20AAP%20leaders.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20April%2C%20the%20vigilance%20department%20terminated%20Bibhav%20Kumar's%20services%20as%20Mr%20Kejriwal's%20personal%20secretary%2C%20citing%20a%202007%20case%20of%20obstructing%20a%20public%20servant%20from%20work.%20He%20approached%20the%20Central%20Administrative%20Tribunal%2C%20but%20did%20not%20get%20any%20relief.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDelhi%20Police%2C%20it%20is%20remand%20note%2C%20has%20questioned%20why%20Bibhav%20Kumar%20was%20at%20the%20Chief%20Minister's%20residence%20on%20May%2013%20--%20when%20the%20alleged%20assault%20on%20Ms%20Maliwal%20took%20place%20--%20despite%20his%20termination.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20Rajya%20Sabha%20MP%20and%20former%20chairperson%20of%20Delhi%20Commission%20for%20Women%2C%20Ms%20Maliwal%20has%20accused%20Bibhav%20Kumar%20of%20assaulting%20her%20during%20a%20visit%20to%20the%20Chief%20Minister's%20residence%20on%20May%2013.%20Kumar%20has%20been%20arrested%20and%20is%20currently%20in%20police%20custody.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20AAP%2C%20which%20had%20earlier%20said%20Bibhav%20Kumar%20had%20misbehaved%20with%20Ms%20Maliwal%20and%20strict%20action%20would%20be%20taken%20against%20him%2C%20has%20now%20said%20its%20MP%20is%20part%20of%20a%20BJP%20conspiracy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAnti-Corruption%20Bureau%20of%20the%20BJP%20has%20filed%20a%20case%20against%20Swati%20Maliwal%20regarding%20the%20illegal%20recruitment%20of%20contractual%20employees%20in%20DCW.%20A%20charge%20sheet%20has%20been%20filed%20and%20the%20time%20of%20conviction%20is%20coming%2C%20we%20believe%20that%20Swati%20Maliwal%20is%20being%20included%20in%20the%20conspiracy%20by%20using%20this%20case.%26quot%3B%20AAP%20leader%20Atishi%20told%20the%20media%20yesterday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Kejriwal%20is%20holding%20a%20protest%20march%20to%20the%20BJP%20headquarters%20today.%20Announcing%20the%20protest%20yesterday%2C%20he%20accused%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20of%20%26quot%3Bplaying%20the%20game%26quot%3B%20of%20sending%20AAP%20leaders%20such%20as%20Manish%20Sisodia%2C%20Satyendar%20Jain%2C%20and%20Sanjay%20Singh%20to%20jail.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThey%20are%20after%20our%20party%20and%20sending%20our%20leaders%20to%20jail%20one%20after%20another...%20Today%20you%20have%20sent%20my%20PA%20(Bibhav%20Kumar)%20to%20jail.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1716105360000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-05%2Fafadnsvo_bibhav-kumar_625x300_19_May_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fsw