cy.%20%26quot%3BAnti-Corruption%20Bureau%20of%20the%20BJP%20has%20filed%20a%20case%20against%20Swati%20Maliwal%20regarding%20the%20illegal%20recruitment%20of%20contractual%20employees%20in%20DCW.%20A%20charge%20sheet%20has%20been%20filed%20and%20the%20time%20of%20conviction%20is%20coming%2C%20we%20believe%20that%20Swati%20Maliwal%20is%20being%20included%20in%20the%20conspiracy%20by%20using%20this%20case%2C%26quot%3B%20AAP%20leader%20and%20Delhi%20Minister%20Atishi%20told%20the%20media%20yesterday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Kejriwal%20has%20announced%20a%20protest%20march%20to%20the%20BJP%20headquarters%20today.%20At%20a%20press%20meet%20yesterday%2C%20he%20accused%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20of%20%26quot%3Bplaying%20the%20game%26quot%3B%20of%20sending%20AAP%20leaders%20such%20as%20Manish%20Sisodia%2C%20Satyendar%20Jain%2C%20and%20Sanjay%20Singh%20to%20jail.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThey%20are%20after%20our%20party%20and%20sending%20our%20leaders%20to%20jail%20one%20after%20another...%20Today%20you%20have%20sent%20my%20PA%20(Bibhav%20Kumar)%20to%20jail%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20the%20BJP%20is%20saying%20they%20will%20send%20AAP%20MP%20Raghav%20Chadha%20and%20Delhi%20ministers%20Atishi%20and%20Saurabh%20Bharadwaj%20to%20jail%20too.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECountering%20Atishi's%20allegations%2C%20Mr%20Sachdeva%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BIt%20would%20have%20been%20better%20if%20she%20(Atishi)%20would've%20spoken%20in%20favour%20of%20Ms%20Maliwal.%20I%20understand%2C%20she%20would've%20done%20this%20to%20save%20her%20seat%20in%20the%20party%2C%20but%20I%20want%20to%20ask%20her%2C%20the%20person%20who%20has%20been%20assaulted%20is%20a%20leader%20of%20AAP%2C%20who%20assaulted%20her%20is%20a%20leader%20of%20AAP%2C%20in%20whose%20house%20she%20was%20assaulted%20is%20also%20leader%20of%20AAP%2C%20the%20whole%20circus%20belongs%20to%20AAP%2C%20how%20is%20BJP%20involved%20in%20the%20matter%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1716104520000%2C%