0the%20phone.%20I%20wish%20they%20had%20tried%20so%20hard%20for%20Manish%20Sisodia.%20If%20he%20was%20here%2C%20maybe%20something%20so%20bad%20would%20not%20have%20happened%20to%20me%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20Mr%20Sisodia%2C%20Delhi's%20former%20Deputy%20Chief%20Minister%2C%20is%20in%20jail%20for%20over%20a%20year%20now%20in%20the%20Delhi%20liquor%20policy%20case.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPolice%20have%20said%20they%20have%20not%20received%20the%20Digital%20Video%20Recorder%20so%20that%20they%20can%20scan%20the%20May%2013%20footage%20as%20part%20of%20their%20probe.%20The%20CCTV%20cameras%20at%20the%20Chief%20Minister's%20residence%20come%20under%20the%20purview%20of%20the%20Public%20Works%20Department%20(PWD).%20A%20junior%20engineer%20from%20the%20department%20has%20given%20police%20one%20video%20in%20a%20pen%20drive%20that%20was%20found%20blank%2C%20the%20remand%20note%20says.%20The%20investigation%20revealed%20that%20the%20junior%20engineer%20does%20not%20have%20access%20to%20the%20DVR%2C%20it%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBibhav%20Kumar%2C%20Chief%20Minister%20Kejriwal's%20close%20aide%2C%20has%20been%20arrested%20and%20remanded%20in%20police%20custody%20for%20five%20days.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDelhi%20Police%20have%20said%20the%20accused%20is%20not%20cooperating%20in%20the%20probe.%20They%20have%20said%20he%20worked%20in%20the%20influential%20position%20of%20the%20Chief%20Minister's%20personal%20secretary%20for%20nine%20years%20and%20can%20tamper%20evidence%20and%20influence%20witnesses.%20The%20remand%20note%20also%20says%20Bibhav%20Kumar%20was%20appointed%20as%20the%20Chief%20Minister's%20personal%20secretary%20in%20February%202015%20and%20removed%20in%20April%20this%20year%20over%20a%202007%20case%20of%20obstructing%20a%20public%20servant%20from%20working.%20Police%20are%20now%20probing%20why%20he%20was%20still%20working%20at%20the%20Chief%20Minister's%20residence.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20remand%20note%20says%20assault%20on%20an%20MP%20is%20a%20very%20serious%20matter%20and%20the%20attack%20could%20have%20turned%20fatal.%20When%20Bibhav%20Kumar%20was%20questioned%20about%20the%20incident%2C%20he%20was%20evasive%2C%20it%20adds.%20The%20statement%20of%20Ms%20Maliwal%20is%20consistent%20with%20her%20medical%20report%2C%20it%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20accused's%20iPhone%2015%20has%20been%20formatted%20and%20needs%20to%20be%20examined%20by%20a%20data%20expert%2C%20police%20have%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBibhav%20Kumar's%20counsel%20Rajiv%20Mohan%20has%20said%20Ms%20Maliwal%20visited%20the%20Chief%20Minister's%20residence%20without%20an%20appointment%20and%20that%20Delhi%20Police%20was%20distorting%20facts.%20He%20also%20said%20she%20filed%20the%20police%20complaint%20on%20May%2016%20--%20three%20days%20after%20the%20incident.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20neither%20did%20Ms%20Maliwal%20seek%20any%20medical%20aid%20after%20calling%20the%20emergency%20helpline%2C%20nor%20did%20the%20station%20house%20officer%20prepare%20any%20medical%20sheet%20after%20meeting%20her.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20lawyer%20alleged%20that%20Ms%20Maliwal%20was%20politicising%20the%20issue%20of%20having%20suffered%20injuries%20and%20giving%20statements%20to%20the%20media.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20its%20rebuttal%2C%20the%20Delhi%20Police%20counsel%20said%20that%20according%20to%20the%20FIR%2C%20Ms%20Maliwal%20was%20%26quot%3Bin%20shock%26quot%3B%20after%20the%20assault%20and%20filed%20a%20police%20complaint%20after%20recovering.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20Rajya%20Sabha%20member%20and%20former%20chief%20of%20the%20Delhi%20Commission%20for%20Women%2C%20Ms%20Maliwal%20has%20alleged%20that%20Bibhav%20Kumar%20had%20slapped%20her%20multiple%20times%20and%20kicked%20her%20during%20the%20May%2013%20incident.%20AAP%20MP%20Sanjay%20Singh%20had%20earlier%20said%20the%20Chief%20Minister's%20aide%20had%20misbehaved%20with%20her%20and%20that%20Mr%20Kejriwal%20will%20take%20strict%20action.%20The%20AAP%20has%20now%20said%20the%20BJP%20has%20made%20Ms%20Maliwal%20part%20of%20a%20conspiracy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAnti-Corruption%20Bureau%20of%20the%20BJP%20has%20filed%20a%20case%20against%20Swati%20Maliwal%20regarding%20the%20illegal%20recruitment%20of%20contractual%20employees%20in%20DCW.%20A%20charge%20sheet%20has%20been%20filed%20and%20the%20time%20of%20conviction%20is%20coming%2C%20we%20believe%20that%20Swati%20Maliwal%20is%20being%20included%20in%20the%20conspiracy%20by%20using%20this%20case.%26quot%3B%20AAP%20leader%20and%20Delhi%20Minister%20Atishi%20told%20the%20media%20yesterday.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1716104160000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-05%2F4fbcgokg_swati-maliwal_625x300_19_May_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fswati-maliwal-assault-case-bibhav-kumar-cctv-footage-may-have-been-tampered-with-delhi-cops-in-swati-maliwal-case-5696154%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20CCTV%20footage%20of%20the%20May%2013%20incident%2C%20in%20which%20AAP%20MP%20Swati%20Maliwal%20was%20allegedly%20assaulted%20at%20Delhi%20Chief%20Minister%20Arvind%20Kejriwal's%20residence%2C%20may%20have%20been%20tampered%20by%20main%20accused%20Bibhav%20Kumar%20to%20destroy%20evidence%2C%20Delhi%20Police%20have%20said.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fswati-maliwal-assault-case-bibhav-kumar-cctv-footage-may-have-been-tampered-with-delhi-cops-in-swati-maliwal-case-5696154%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fswati-maliwal-assault-case-bibhav-kumar-cctv-footage-may-have-been-tampered-with-delhi-cops-in-swati-maliwal-case-5696154%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fswati-maliwal-assault-case-bibhav-kumar-cctv-footage-may-have-been-tampered-with-delhi-cops-in-swati-maliwal-case-5696154%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Pakistani%20doctor%20with%20loaded%20pistol%20on%20duty