ore%20than%20%C2%A3120%20million%20over%20the%20past%20year.%20Overtaking%20the%20UK's%20monarch%20King%20Charles%2C%20their%20wealth%20witnessed%20a%20jump%20from%20last%20year's%20%C2%A3529%20million%20to%20%C2%A3651%20million%20in%202024.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20Sunak%20has%20occupied%20245th%20place%20on%20the%20list%2C%20King%20Charles%20holds%20258th%20rank%2C%20after%20his%20wealth%20grew%20from%20%C2%A3600%20million%20to%20%C2%A3610%20million%20in%20the%20same%20period.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20per%20a%20report%20in%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.mirror.co.uk%2Fmoney%2Fsunday-times-rich-list-wealth-32829413%5C%22%3EMirror%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20couple's%20fortune%20is%20driven%20largely%20by%20Akshata%20Murty's%20stake%20in%20Infosys%2C%20founded%20by%20her%20father%2C%20Narayana%20Murthy.%20It%20is%20worth%20noting%20that%20they%20are%20the%20wealthiest%20residents%20of%2010%20Downing%20Street%20in%20history.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Fuk-politics-69027955%5C%22%3EBBC%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20Sunaks'%20wealth%20also%20ranked%20higher%20than%20that%20of%20the%20late%20Queen%20in%202022.%20This%20was%20after%20Elizabeth%20II's%20personal%20fortune%20was%20evaluated%20at%20%C2%A3370%20million.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20the%20report%20added%20that%20estimating%20the%20personal%20fortunes%20of%20monarchs%20is%20tricky.%20It%20must%20be%20noted%20that%20the%20wider%20wealth%20of%20the%20monarchy%2C%20which%20includes%20various%20estates%20and%20palaces%2C%20has%20been%20estimated%20at%20dozens%20of%20billions%20of%20pounds.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20this%2C%20the%20UK%20Prime%20Minister%20also%20became%20the%20first%20front-line%20politician%20to%20feature%20on%20the%20Sunday%20Times'%20annual%20wealth%20list%20in%20its%2035-year%20history.%20This%20includes%20Sunak%20appearing%20on%20the%20list%20as%20chancellor%20in%20the%202022%20edition%20when%20the%20family's%20wealth%20was%20estimated%20at%20%C2%A3730%20million.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Fsunday-times-rich-list-rishi-sunak-leapfrogs-king-charles-in-latest-rankings-13137037%5C%22%3ESky%20News%3C%2Fa%3E%20noted%20that%20the%20combined%20wealth%20of%20the%20list's%20350%20wealthiest%20people%20amounts%20to%20over%20%C2%A3795%20billion%2C%20which%20is%20larger%20than%20the%20gross%20domestic%20product%20(GDP)%20of%20Poland.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20the%20Chairperson%20of%20the%20Hinduja%20Group%20Gopichand%20Hinduja%20topped%20the%20list%20again%20in%202024%2C%20with%20his%20fortune%20touching%20%C2%A337.196%20billion.%20Last%20year%20also%2C%20Mr%20Hinduja%20occupied%20first%20place%20on%20the%20list.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1716103680000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-02%2F555mmtgg_king-charles-rishi-sunak-afp_625x300_22_February_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fuk-pm-rishi-sunak-wife-akshata-murty-richer-than-king-charles-new-list-shows-5696606%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22UK%20Prime%20Minister%20Rishi%20Sunak%20and%20his%20wife%20Akshata%20Murty's%20personal%20wealth%20overtook%20that%20of%20King%20Charles%2C%20reported%20the%20latest%20Sunday%20Times%20Rich%20List.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fuk-pm-rishi-sunak-wife-akshata-murty-richer-than-king-charles-new-list-shows-5696606%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fuk-pm-rishi-sunak-wife-akshata-murty-richer-than-king-charles-new-list-shows-5696606%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fuk-pm-rishi-sunak-wife-akshata-murty-richer-than-king-charles-new-list-shows-5696606%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Mubi%20Acquires%20Magnus%20von%20Horn%E2%80%99s%20Chilling%20Cannes%20Competition%20Entry