ver%20won%20with%20overconfidence.%20I%20think%20big%2C%20but%20always%20remain%20grounded%2C%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20Prime%20Minister%20said%20in%20an%20exclusive%20interview%20with%20NDTV's%20Editor-in-Chief%20Sanjay%20Pugalia.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Prime%20Minister%2C%20who%20has%20tasked%20his%20ministers%20to%20come%20up%20with%20an%20action%20plan%20for%20the%20first%20100%20days%20of%20his%20new%20government%2C%20told%20NDTV%20the%20route%20to%20success%20-%20stressing%20on%20scope%2C%20scale%2C%20speed%20and%20skill.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%C2%A0%26quot%3BThe%20scope%20should%20be%20very%20big%2C%20it%20shouldn't%20be%20in%20parts.%20The%20second%20thing%20is%20scale%2C%20which%20should%20also%20be%20large.%20The%20speed%20should%20be%20in%20sync%20with%20these%20two.%20So%2C%20scope%2C%20scale%20and%20speed%2C%20and%20then%20there%20should%20be%20skill.%20If%20we%20can%20get%20these%20four%20things%20together%2C%20I%20believe%20we%20can%20achieve%20a%20lot%2C%26quot%3B%20PM%20Modi%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20about%20his%20macro-level%20thinking%2C%20the%20Prime%20Minister%20said%20the%20fact%20that%20the%20Congress%20and%20the%20INDIA%20alliance%20have%20not%20declared%20a%20PM%20candidate%20deprives%20the%20voters%20of%20the%20opportunity%20to%20assess%20him%20or%20her.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20also%20said%20that%20every%20cabinet%20note%20related%20to%20a%20Bill%20now%20comes%20with%20a%20global%20standards%20report%20so%20that%20the%20legislation%20can%20be%20aligned%20to%20the%20best%20practices%20worldwide.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThese%20days%2C%20a%20tradition%20has%20started%20in%20my%20cabinet.%20Whenever%20a%20Bill%20to%20be%20introduced%20in%20Parliament%20comes%20before%20the%20cabinet%2C%20a%20global%20standards%20note%20comes%20with%20it.%20This%20note%20mentions%20which%20country%20is%20performing%20the%20best%20in%20that%20particular%20field%2C%20what%20are%20the%20rules%20there%20and%20how%20we%20can%20achieve%20that.%20So%2C%20we%20have%20to%20match%20every%20cabinet%20note%20with%20global%20standards%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections%20began%20on%20April%2019%20and%20the%20fifth%20phase%20of%20polling%20will%20take%20place%20tomorrow.%20Counting%20will%20be%20held%20on%20June%204.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETune%20in%20at%208%20pm%20today%20to%20watch%20the%20interview%2C%20which%20will%20be%20aired%20across%20the%20NDTV%20network.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1716102300000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-05%2F85jg2a5g_modi_625x300_19_May_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fi-think-big-but-always-remain-grounded-pm-narendra-modi-to-ndtv-5696427%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20BJP%2C%20under%20the%20leadership%20of%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%2C%20has%20set%20a%20target%20of%20winning%20370%20seats%20for%20itself%20and%20400%20for%20the%20NDA%20in%20the%20ongoing%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections%2C%20four%20phases%20of%20which%20are%20over.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fi-think-big-but-always-remain-grounded-pm-narendra-modi-to-ndtv-5696427%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fi-think-big-but-always-remain-grounded-pm-narendra-modi-to-ndtv-5696427%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fi-think-big-but-always-remain-grounded-pm-narendra-modi-to-ndtv-5696427%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22FPIs%20withdraw%20Rs%2028%2C200%20crore%20from%20Indian%20equities%20on%20election%20jitters%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1716101959000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fbsmedia.business-standard.com%2F_media%2Fbs%2Fimg%2Farticle%2F2024-04%2F17%2Fthumb%2Ffeaturecrop%2F400X400%2F1713331050-5792.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Fmarke