Mass%20Wedding%20For%20Nigeria%20Orphans%20Sparks%20Uproar%2C%20Some%20Feared%20To%20Be%20Minors%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EA%20Nigerian%20state%20lawmaker's%20plan%20to%20sponsor%20the%20marriage%20of%20100%20brides%20orphaned%20by%20violence%20has%20sparked%20a%20row%20over%20religious%20and%20cultural%20norms.%20According%20to%20%3Cem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Farticles%2Fc3gqvzql9ylo%5C%22%3EBBC%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20some%20of%20these%20orphans%2C%20feared%20to%20be%20underage%20girls%2C%20are%20set%20to%20be%20married%20off%20on%2024%20May%20in%20the%20north-western%20state%20of%20Niger.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20wedding%20is%20being%20sponsored%20by%20Abdulmalik%20Sarkindaji%2C%20the%20speaker%20of%20the%20national%20assembly%20in%20the%20largely%20Muslim%20north-western%20state%20of%20Niger.%20However%2C%20critics%20have%20expressed%20concern%20that%20some%20girls%20may%20be%20underage%20or%20being%20forced%20to%20comply%20for%20financial%20gain.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUju%20Kennedy-Ohanenye%2C%20the%20federal%20women's%20affairs%20minister%2C%20called%20the%20ceremony%20unacceptable%20and%20demanded%20an%20investigation%20into%20the%20ages%20of%20the%20brides%20and%20whether%20they%20had%20consented%20to%20marriage.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20said%3A%20''I%20have%20written%20a%20petition%20to%20the%20police%20...%20and%20I%20have%20filed%20a%20case%20for%20an%20injunction%20to%20stop%20him%20from%20whatever%20he%20is%20planning%20to%20do.''%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20senior%20special%20assistant%20to%20the%20presidency%20on%20community%20engagement%20has%20also%20objected.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20am%20not%20against%20conducting%20marriage%20for%20orphans%20above%2018%20years%20of%20age%20if%20they%20give%20their%20consent%20to%20the%20marriage%2C%20But%20I%20am%20against%20underaged%20marriage.%20Let%20children%20be%20children%2C''%20she%20wrote%20on%20X.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESeveral%C2%A0Nigerian%20Human%20rights%20groups%20have%20also%20launched%20a%20petition%20to%20stop%20the%20mass%20wedding%20plan.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E''It%20is%20our%20firm%20belief%20that%20every%20child%2C%20regardless%20of%20their%20circumstances%2C%20has%20the%20right%20to%20education%2C%20protection%2C%20and%20a%20safe%20upbringing.%20The%20decision%20to%20marry%20off%20these%20vulnerable%20girls%20under%20the%20guise%20of%20preventing%20fornication%20is%20not%20only%20morally%20reprehensible%20but%20also%20a%20violation%20of%20their%20fundamental%20rights%20as%20enshrined%20in%20the%20Nigerian%20Constitution%2C''%20a%20petition%20on%3Cem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.change.org%2Fp%2Fpetition-against-forced-marriage-of-orphaned-girls-in-niger-state%5C%22%3E%20Change.org%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%20read.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E''We%20urge%20the%20Niger%20State%20Government%20to%20uphold%20its%20duty%20to%20protect%20the%20rights%20of%20these%20orphaned%20girls%20by%20prioritizing%20their%20education%20and%20well-being.%20Rather%20than%20subjecting%20them%20to%20forced%20marriages%2C%20we%20call%20upon%20the%20government%20to%20provide%20adequate%20support%2C%20including%20access%20to%20quality%20education%20and%20proper%20care%20in%20well-managed%20orphanage%20homes%2C''%20the%20petition%20notes.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFollowing%20the%20public%20outrage%2C%20Speaker%20Sarkindaji%20has%20announced%20his%20withdrawal%20from%20the%20ceremony.%20However%2C%20the%20Imams%20Forum%20of%20Niger%20said%20that%20the%20marriage%20ceremony%20should%20go%20ahead%2C%20insisting%20that%20the%20girls%20are%20not%20below%20the%2018.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChild%20marriages%20are%20most%20common%20in%20the%20northern%20part%20of%20the%20country%2C%20among%20poor%2C%20rural%20households.%20It%20is%20seen%20as%20a%20way%20to%20reduce%20their%20families'%20financial%20burdens%20or%20to%20improve%20political%20and%20social%20alliances.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1716099840000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22ht