inesh-karthik-reveals-ms-dhonis-role-in-rcbs-win-virat-kohlis-reaction-cant-be-missed-watch-5696190%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Dinesh%20Karthik%2C%20in%20a%20video%20shared%20by%20RCB%20on%20social%20media%2C%20explained%20MS%20Dhoni's%20role%20in%20RCB's%20victory%20against%20CSK.%20Virat%20Kohli's%20reaction%20said%20it%20all.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fipl-2024%2Fdinesh-karthik-reveals-ms-dhonis-role-in-rcbs-win-virat-kohlis-reaction-cant-be-missed-watch-5696190%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fipl-2024%2Fdinesh-karthik-reveals-ms-dhonis-role-in-rcbs-win-virat-kohlis-reaction-cant-be-missed-watch-5696190%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fipl-2024%2Fdinesh-karthik-reveals-ms-dhonis-role-in-rcbs-win-virat-kohlis-reaction-cant-be-missed-watch-5696190%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22PM%20Modi%20Explains%20Why%20He%20Believes%20BJP%20Will%20Get%20%26quot%3BHistoric%20Mandate%26quot%3B%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EPitching%20his%20government%20as%20sensitive%20to%20the%20dreams%20and%20aspirations%20of%20the%20millions%20of%20Indians%2C%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20underlined%20how%20the%20trust%20shown%20by%20voters%20will%20help%20his%20party%2C%20BJP%2C%20win%20a%20%26quot%3Bhistoric%20mandate%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20country%20is%20in%20the%20middle%20of%20a%20marathon%20general%20election%20spread%20over%20six%20weeks%2C%20the%20second%20biggest%20since%20the%20general%20election%20of%201951-52%2C%20with%20three%20more%20rounds%20to%20go.%20There%20are%20seven%20phases.%20The%20votes%20will%20be%20counted%20on%20June%204.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3B%3Cem%3ESarkaar%20ke%20prati%20bharosa%20hai%20aur%20isiliye%20main%20kehta%20hoon%20ki%20is%20chunaav%20main%20BJP%20historically%20ek%20bahut%20bada%20record%20set%20karne%20wali%20hai%3C%2Fem%3E%20(There%20is%20great%20trust%20in%20this%20government.%20It%20is%20for%20this%20reason%20I%20say%20that%20the%20BJP%20will%20get%20a%20historic%20mandate%20and%20will%20set%20a%20record)%2C%26quot%3B%20PM%20Modi%20said%20in%20an%20interview%20with%20NDTV's%20Editor-in-Chief%20Sanjay%20Pugalia.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPolling%20is%20over%20in%20the%20four%20southern%20states%2C%20where%20the%20BJP%2C%20led%20by%20the%20Prime%20Minister%2C%20has%20made%20a%20big%20push%20to%20win%20over%20voters.%20The%20south%20remains%20the%20BJP's%20Achilees'%20heel.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%C2%A0%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%26quot%3B%3Cem%3EAaj%20desh%20ko%20lag%20raha%20hai%20ki%20aaj%20ek%20aisi%20sarkar%20hai%20jis%20sarkaar%20ko%20hamare%20dukhon%20ki%20chinta%20hai%2C%20hamare%20sapno%20ka%20usko%20andaaz%20hai%20aur%20jo%20hamare%20saamarth%20ko%20hamesha%20badhane%20ka%20prayaas%20karti%20hai%3C%2Fem%3E%20(Today%20the%20country%20feels%20that%20there%20is%20such%20a%20government%20which%20is%20concerned%20about%20our%20sorrows%2C%20respects%20our%20dreams%20and%20always%20tries%20to%20show%20our%20strength)%2C%26quot%3B%20PM%20Modi%2C%2073%2C%20told%20the%20channel.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20southern%20states%20-%20Tamil%20Nadu%2C%20Kerala%2C%20Karnataka%2C%20Andhra%20Pradesh%2C%20and%20Telangana%20-%20with%20Puducherry's%20one%20seat%20sends%20130%20MPs%20to%20the%20Lower%20House.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202019%20the%20BJP%20scored%20only%2029%20of%20these%20seats%2C%20of%20which%2025%20were%20from%20Karnataka%20and%20the%20rest%20from%20Telangana.%20The%20party%20failed%20to%20open%20its%20account%20in%20Kerala%2C%20Tamil%20Nadu%2C%20Andhra%20Pradesh%2C%20and%20Puducherry.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP%2C%20which%20won%20303%20seats%20in%202019%2C%20has%20set%20itself%20a%20mammoth%20target%20of%20370%20this%20time%20and%20with%20help%20from%20allies%2C%20it%20aims%20go%20%26quot%3B%3Cem%3E400%20paar%3C%2Fem%3E%26quot%3B.%20The%20Congress%2C%20depleted%20by%20poll%20losses%20and%20big%20defections%2C%20is%20part%20of%20the%20Opposition%20bloc%20INDIA%20taking%20on%20the%20BJP.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3B%3Cem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fbjp-has-the-upper-hand-everyone-knows-it-pm-modi-to-ndtv-on-2024-polls-5693492%5C%22%3EHamara%20palda%20bahut%20bhari%20hai%20%3C%2Fa%3Eusme%20mujhe%20kuch%20kehne%20ki%20jaroorat%20nahi%20hai.%20Hamara%20palda%20bhaari%20hai%2C%20har%20koi%20jaanta%20hai%3C%2Fem%3E%20(The%20scales%20are%20heavily%20tilted%20in%20our%20favour.%20I%20don't%20have%20to%20say%20anything%20about%20that.%20We%20have%20the%20upper%20hand.%20And%20everyone%20knows%20it)%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20Prime%20Minister%2C%20contesting%20from%20Varanasi%20in%20Uttar%20Pradesh%2C%20underscored.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP%20swept%20the%20politically%20prized%20state%20of%20Uttar%20Pradesh%2C%20which%20sends%20most%20number%20of%20MPs%20(80)%20to%20Lok%20Sabha%2C%20in%202014%20and%202019%2C%20winning%2071%20and%2062%20seats%2C%20respectively.%20The%20BJP%20won%20handsomely%20in%20the%20big%20Hindi%20heartland%20states%20sweeping%20Rajasthan%2C%20Gujarat%20and%20won%2028%20out%20of%2029%20seats%20in%20Madhya%20Pradesh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECongress%2C%20the%20principal%20opposition%20party%2C%20is%20contesting%2017%20seats%20in%20UP%20this%20time.%20It%20is%20in%20alliance%20with%20Akhilesh%20Yadav-led%20Samajwadi%20Party%2C%20which%20is%20contesting%20on%2063%20seats.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPM%20Modi%2C%20who%20says%20the%20country%20will%20become%20the%20third%20largest%20economy%20in%20his%20third%20term%2C%20spelt%20out%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fndtv-mega-exclusive-when-scope-scale-and-speed-meet-skill-pm-modis-recipe-for-success-5693189%5C%22%3E'four-S'%20mantra%20for%20the%20country%20to%20achieve%20big%20things%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20scope%20should%20be%20very%20big%2C%20it%20shouldn't%20be%20in%20parts%2C%20and%20the%20second%20thing%20is%20scale%2C%20which%20should%20also%