.com%2Fweb-series%2Fnews%2Fkorean%2Fpark-hyung-sik-talks-about-friendship-with-bts-v-in-wooga-squad%2Farticleshow%2F110245074.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22PM%20Modi%20Reveals%20%26quot%3BNew%20Tradition%26quot%3B%20In%20His%20Cabinet%20To%20Make%20India%20Better%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EEvery%20cabinet%20note%20related%20to%20a%20Bill%20now%20comes%20with%20a%20global%20standards%20report%20so%20that%20the%20legislation%20can%20be%20aligned%20to%20the%20best%20practices%20worldwide%2C%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20has%20told%20NDTV%20in%20an%20exclusive%20interview.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20to%20NDTV's%20editor-in-chief%20Sanjay%20Pugalia%2C%20the%20Prime%20Minister%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BThese%20days%2C%20a%20tradition%20has%20started%20in%20my%20cabinet.%20Whenever%20a%20Bill%20to%20be%20introduced%20in%20Parliament%20comes%20before%20the%20cabinet%2C%20a%20global%20standards%20note%20comes%20with%20it.%20This%20note%20mentions%20which%20country%20is%20performing%20the%20best%20in%20that%20particular%20field%2C%20what%20are%20the%20rules%20there%20and%20how%20we%20can%20achieve%20that.%20So%2C%20we%20have%20to%20match%20every%20cabinet%20note%20with%20global%20standards.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20has%20become%20a%20habit%20for%20the%20bureaucracy%20now.%20Just%20saying%20our%20(plan)%20is%20the%20best%20in%20the%20world%20is%20not%20enough.%20Say%20who%20is%20doing%20the%20best%20in%20world%20and%20where%20we%20are%20and%20how%20we%20can%20get%20there%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20Prime%20Minister%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Prime%20Minister%20also%20expressed%20confidence%20that%20the%20BJP%20is%20set%20to%20score%20a%20record%20win%20in%20the%20ongoing%20general%20election%2C%20four%20phases%20of%20which%20are%20over.%20Everyone%2C%20he%20said%2C%20knows%20that%20the%20scales%20are%20tilted%20in%20favour%20of%20the%20BJP%20and%20the%20NDA%20alliance.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe