20initially%20presented%20the%20'Game%20Of%20Thrones'%20star%20with%20several%20difficulties.%20She%20found%20it%20annoying%20that%20everything%20was%20so%20far%20away%20as%20it%20required%20her%20to%20travel%20for%20at%20least%20forty%20minutes%20in%20order%20to%20visit%20someone%20and%20referred%20to%20the%20way%20of%20living%20as%20%26quot%3Bisolating%26quot%3B.%20%26quot%3BYou%20can't%20just%20bump%20into%20someone%20at%20a%20bar%20there%2C%20you%20have%20to%20drive%2040%20minutes%20with%20an%20intention%20of%20seeing%20someone%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said%20in%20an%20interview%20with%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.vogue.co.uk%2Farticle%2Fsophie-turner-british-vogue-interview%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EVogue%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGetting%20married%20to%20a%20Jonas%20brother%20meant%20joining%20a%20bigger%20family%20that%20included%20two%20sisters-in-law.%20However%2C%20the%2029-year-old%20did%20not%20feel%20comfortable%20with%20the%20attention%20that%20followed.%20%26quot%3BThere%20was%20a%20lot%20of%20attention%20on%20the%20three%20brothers%20and%20the%20wives.%20Well%2C%20we%20were%20always%20called%20the%20wives%2C%20and%20I%20hated%20that.%20It%20was%20kind%20of%20this%20plus-one%20feeling.%20And%20that's%20nothing%20to%20do%20with%20him%20-%20in%20no%20way%20did%20he%20make%20me%20feel%20that%20-%20it%20was%20just%20that%20the%20perception%20of%20us%20was%20as%20the%20groupies%20in%20the%20band%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20their%20decision%20to%20relocate%20their%20small%20family%20to%20Miami%20in%202021%20only%20heightened%20those%20sentiments%20of%20isolation.%20According%20to%20her%2C%20it%20was%20nothing%20less%20than%20cultural%20shock%20for%20the%20performer.%20%26quot%3BWe%20were%20in%20this%20community%20full%20of%2050-year-old%20men%2C%20so%20imagine%20trying%20to%20make%20friends%20on%20the%20dog%20walk.%20I%20just%20felt%20like%20a%20little%20bird%20trapped%20in%20a%20gilded%20cage.%20It%20was%20amazing%2C%20yes%2C%20but%20I%20didn't%20have%20any%20friends%20there%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFurther%2C%20Ms%20Turner%20was%20growing%20more%20uneasy%20about%20America's%20gun%20violence%20epidemic%20as%20a%20mother.%20She%20was%20devastated%20when%20she%20learned%20of%20the%20Uvalde%20killings%20in%202022.%20She%20told%20the%20outlet%2C%20%26quot%3BI%20couldn't%20fathom%20being%20a%20mother%20of%20one%20of%20those%20children%20knowing%20that%20this%20was%20something%20your%20country%20could%20fix%2C%20that%20they'd%20rather%20have%20rights%20to%20guns%20than%20give%20kids%20a%20right%20to%20life.%20Meanwhile%2C%20women%20in%20the%20US%20are%20being%20stripped%20of%20their%20rights%2C%20left%2C%20right%20and%20centre.%20It%20all%20contributed%20to%20this%20feeling%20of%20I%20have%20to%20get%20out%2C%20I%20have%20to%20get%20out.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJoe%20Jonas%20and%20Sophie%20Turner%20announced%20their%20split%20in%20September%202023%20after%20four%20years%20of%20marriage.%20They%20tied%20the%20knot%20in%202019%20after%20nearly%20three%20years%20of%20dating.%20They%20issued%20a%20joint%20statement%20which%20read%2C%20%26quot%3BStatement%20from%20the%20two%20of%20us%3A%20%26quot%3BAfter%20four%20wonderful%20years%20of%20marriage%20we%20have%20mutually%20decided%20to%20amicably%20end%20our%20marriage.%20There%20are%20many%20speculative%20narratives%20as%20to%20why%20but%2C%20truly%20this%20is%20a%20united%20decision%20and%20we%20sincerely%20hope%20that%20everyone%20can%20respect%20our%20wishes%20for%20privacy%20for%20us%20and%20our%20children.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20comments%20emerged%20in%20the%20days%20that%20followed%2C%20calling%20her%20a%20%26quot%3Bbad%20mum%26quot%3B%20since%20she%20was%20an%20extrovert%20as%20compared%20to%20her%20husband.%20Recalling%20the%20harrowing%20time%2C%20she%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BI%20mean%2C%20those%20were%20the%20worst%20few%20days%20of%20my%20life.%20I%20remember%20I%20was%20on%20set%2C%20I%20was%20contracted%20to%20be%20on%20set%20for%20another%20two%20weeks%2C%20so%20I%20couldn't%20leave.%20My%20kids%20were%20in%20the%20States%20and%20I%20couldn't%20get%20to%20them%20because%20I%20had%20to%20finish%20Joan.%20And%20all%20these%20articles%20started%20coming%20out.%20It%20hurt%20because%20I%20really%20do%20completely%20torture%20myself%20over%20every%20move%20I%20make%20as%20a%20mother%20-%20mum%20guilt%20is%20so%20real!%20I%20just%20kept%20having%20to%20say%20to%20myself%2C%20'None%20of%20this%20is%20true.%20You%20are%20a%20good%20mum%20and%20you've%20never%20been%20a%20partier.'%26quot%3B%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1716097080000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-05%2Fvl6tijio_sophie_625x300_19_May_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ffeature%2Fsophie-turner-says-life-after-marriage-with-joe-jonas-was-isolating-5696343%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20couple's%20decision%20to%20relocate%20their%20small%20family%20to%20Miami%20in%202021%20only%20heightened%20those%20sentiments%20of%20isolation.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ffeature%2Fsophie-turner-says-life-after-marriage-with-joe-jonas-was-isolating-5696343%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ffeature%2Fsophie-turner-says-life-after-marriage-with-joe-jonas-was-isolating-5696343%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ffeature%2Fsophie-turner-says-life-after-marriage-with-joe-jonas-was-isolating-5696343%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Mcap%20of%208%20of%20most%20valued%20firms%20climbs%20Rs%201.47%20trn%3B%20LIC%2C%20RIL%20major%20gainers%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1716096968000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fbsmedia.business-standard.com%2F_media%2Fbs%2Fimg%2Farticle%2F2024-04%2F10%2Fthumb%2Ffitandfill%2F400X400%2F1712718107-734.jpg%22%2C%22o