%3Emahiwaga%3C%2Fem%3E%C2%A0%5Bmysterious%5D%20backgrounds%2C%20an%20asset%20inserted%20by%20China%20into%20our%20government%20to%20have%20a%20heavy%20influence%20in%20Philippine%20politics%3F''%20Senator%20Risa%20Hontiveros%20asked%20during%20a%20press%20conference%20on%20May%208.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20data-qa%3D%5C%22Component-Component%5C%22%3ELittle%20is%20known%20about%20her%20background%2C%20which%20is%20unusual%20in%20rural%20Philippines.%20Her%20family%20name%2C%20Guo%2C%20is%20also%20not%20among%20the%20common%20family%20names%20of%20Filipinos%20with%20Chinese%20lineage.%C2%A0During%20the%20hearing%2C%20she%20also%20gave%20vague%20answers%20about%20her%20background%2C%20including%20basic%20personal%20questions%20about%20her%20family%2C%20school%20and%20similar%20facts%2C%20raising%20suspicions.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20data-qa%3D%5C%22Component-Component%5C%22%3EMs%20Guo%20admitted%20that%20her%20birth%20certificate%20was%20registered%20with%20local%20authorities%20only%20when%20she%20turned%2017.%20When%20asked%20the%20reason%20for%20this%2C%20she%20said%20this%20was%20because%20she%20was%20born%20in%20a%20house%2C%20not%20in%20a%20hospital%20or%20clinic.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20data-qa%3D%5C%22Component-Component%5C%22%3EShe%20further%20said%20she%20was%20home-schooled%20exclusively%20inside%20the%20family%20compound%2C%20but%20could%20not%20remember%20the%20name%20of%20her%20home%20school%20organisation%20and%20names%20of%20teachers%20except%20one.%C2%A0She%20said%20her%20father%20is%20Filipino%2C%20but%20in%20business%20records%2C%20her%20father%20was%20identified%20as%20a%20Chinese%20citizen.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20data-qa%3D%5C%22Component-Component%5C%22%3ESenator%20Hontiveros%20described%20her%20as%20someone%20who%20''figuratively%20came%20out%20of%20nowhere%20and%20afterwards%20became%20mayor''.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20data-qa%3D%5C%22Component-Component%5C%22%3EMeanwhile%2C%20Philippine%20President%20Ferdinand%20Marcos%20Junior%20told%20journalists%20that%20he%20supported%20the%20probe.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E''I%20know%20all%20the%20politicians%20from%20Tarlac%20%5Bprovince%5D%2C%20no%20one%20knows%20her.%20So%2C%20we%20are%20wondering%20where%20she%20came%20from.%20We%20don't%20know.%20That's%20why%20an%20investigation%20is%20really%20needed%2C''%20he%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20will%20tighten%20the%20enforcement%20of%20the%20law.%20The%20laws%20are%20there%2C%20the%20problem%20is%20that%20some%20people%20think%20these%20people%20can%20bring%20money%2C%20or%20they%20will%20take%20bribes%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20Ms%20Guo%C2%A0has%20maintained%20she%20is%20a%20Philippine%20citizen%20and%20denied%20her%20involvement%20in%20unlawful%20gaming.%C2%A0She%20could%20be%20charged%20with%20perjury%20if%20it%20was%20proved%20she%20was%20not%20a%20Filipino%20citizen.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1716095700000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-05%2F693b379o_alice-leal-guo_625x300_19_May_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fphilippine-town-mayor-accused-of-being-a-chinese-spy-no-one-knows-where-she-came-from-5696116%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22During%20a%20Senate%20hearing%2C%20the%2035-year-old%20mayor%20failed%20to%20provide%20details%20about%20her%20early%20life%20and%20background%2C%20fuelling%20suspicions%20about%20her%20nationality.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fphilippine-town-mayor-accused-of-being-a-chinese-spy-no-one-knows-where-she-came-from-5696116%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fphilippine-town-mayor-accused-of-being-a-chinese-spy-no-one-knows-where-she-came-from-5696116%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fphilippine-town-mayor-accused-of-being-a-chinese-spy-no-one-knows-