96009%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BI%20Know%20That%20This%20Year...%26quot%3B%3A%20CSK%20Coach%20On%20MS%20Dhoni's%20Potential%20Retirement%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EChennai%20Super%20Kings%20(CSK)%20bowling%20consultant%20Eric%20Simons%20lavished%20praise%20on%20the%20franchise's%20icon%20MS%20Dhoni%20and%20feels%20that%20speculating%20about%20the%20veteran's%20future%20is%20%26quot%3Bcrazy%26quot%3B.%20CSK's%20title%20defence%20ended%20after%20a%2027-run%20loss%20to%20RCB%20on%20Saturday%20at%20the%20M%20Chinnaswamy%20Stadium.%20All%20eyes%20were%20on%20MS%20Dhoni%2C%20thinking%20whether%20he%20would%20announce%20his%20retirement%20after%20CSK's%20campaign%20in%20the%20Indian%20Premier%20League%202024%20ended.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESimons%20has%20witnessed%20Dhoni%20with%20the%20Indian%20team%20during%20his%20stint%20as%20a%20bowling%20consultant%20in%202010.%20After%20the%20game%2C%20Simons%20pinpointed%20the%20various%20attributes%20that%20Dhoni%20offers%20to%20the%20team.%20He%20feels%20that%20with%20the%20simplicity%20Dhoni%20perceives%20the%20game%20is%20what%20cricketers%20should%20strive%20for.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere%20are%20so%20many%20memories%20of%20MS%20Dhoni%2C%20the%20knocks%20that%20he%20plays%20get%20you%20out%20of%20trouble.%20I%20was%20in%20the%20dugout%20and%20said%20it%20was%20incredible%20we%20are%20in%20a%20situation%20with%20our%20backs%20against%20the%20wall%20and%20he%20is%20at%20the%20wicket%20you%20just%20don't%20stop%20believing%20he%20can%20win%20for%20you%2C%20So%20I%20think%20that%20is%20one%20of%20the%20things%20that%20he%20brings%20to%20the%20group%20is%20the%20incredible%20self-belief.%20But%20he%20has%20a%20very%20simple%20structure%20and%20understanding%20of%20the%20game.%20I%20think%20that's%20what%20a%20lot%20of%20cricketers%20should%20strive%20for%20to%2C%20really%20understand%20the%20game%20and%20he%20does%20and%20he%20helps%20guys%20with%20that%20sort%20of%20information%20and%20knowledge%20