oss%20eight%20states%20and%20Union%20Territories%20will%20vote%20in%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fls-polls-up-fifth-phase-to-witness-high-profile-contests-5666896%5C%22%3EPhase%205%20of%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20May%2020.%20With%20polling%20completed%20for%2070%25%20of%20the%20total%20Lok%20Sabha%20seats%2C%20the%20battle%20now%20enters%20the%20consolidation%20phase%20for%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fvideo%2Fbjp-has-the-upper-hand-everyone-knows-it-pm-modi-to-ndtv-s-sanjay-pugalia-on-lok-sabha-elections-202-785837%5C%22%3EBharatiya%20Janata%20Party%3C%2Fa%3E%20(BJP)%20in%20battleground%20states.%20%C2%A0Since%20the%20party%20won%20a%20majority%20of%20these%20seats%20along%20with%20its%20allies%20in%202019%2C%20the%20challenge%20for%20the%20National%20Democratic%20Alliance%20(NDA)%20is%20maintaining%20its%20tally%20and%20preventing%20any%20significant%20slippages.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20phase%20will%20see%20polling%20in%20five%20seats%20each%20in%20Bihar%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ftopic%2Fodisha%5C%22%3EOdisha%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20three%20in%20Jharkhand%2C%20one%20each%20in%20Jammu%20%26amp%3B%20Kashmir%20and%20Ladakh%2C%2013%20in%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fvideo%2Fmaharashtra-rallies-face-off-mva-versus-mahayuti-785541%5C%22%3EMaharashtra%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%2014%20in%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20and%20seven%20in%20West%20Bengal.%20This%20phase%20will%20also%20mark%20the%20end%20of%20voting%20in%20Maharashtra%20and%20the%20western%20region.%20Thereafter%2C%20the%20battle%20remains%20in%20only%20the%20Hindi%20heartland%20and%20eastern%20India.%20Additionally%2C%20Odisha%20will%20also%20be%20simultaneously%20voting%20for%2035%20assembly%20seats%20on%20May%2020.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20key%20high-profile%20candidates%20in%20this%20phase%20are%20Rajnath%20Singh%20(Lucknow)%2C%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20(Raebareli)%2C%20Piyush%20Goyal%20(Mumbai%20North)%2C%20Chirag%20Paswan%20(Hajipur)%20and%20Omar%20Abdullah%20(Baramulla).%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Seat%20Splits%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP%20is%20contesting%2040%20seats%20and%20its%20allies%20are%20fighting%20in%20nine.%20This%20includes%20the%20six%20seats%20the%20Eknath%20Shinde-led%20Shiv%20Sena%20is%20vying%20for.%20In%20contrast%2C%20the%20Congress%20is%20contesting%20on%20just%2018%20seats%2C%20leaving%2031%20for%20its%20allies.%20The%20Samajwadi%20Party%20(SP)%20is%20contesting%2010%20seats%2C%20the%20Uddhav%20Thackeray-led%20Shiv%20Sena%20eight%2C%20Sharad%20Pawar's%20Nationalist%20Congress%20Party%20(NCP)%20two%2C%20and%20the%20Rashtriya%20Janata%20Dal%20(RJD)%20four.%20The%20Bahujan%20Samaj%20Party%20(BSP)%2C%20meanwhile%2C%20is%20in%20the%20battle%20for%2046%20seats%2C%20the%20Biju%20Janata%20Dal%20(BJD)%20for%20five%2C%20and%20the%20Trinamool%20Congress%20(TMC)%20seven.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20NDTV%20Data%20Centre%2C%20in%202019%2C%20the%20BJP%20won%2032%20of%20the%2049%20seats%20that%20will%20vote%20on%20Monday%3B%20the%20Congress%20when%20on%20a%20single%20seat%2C%20the%20BJD%20two%2C%20BJP%20allies%20seven%2C%20and%20Congress%20allies%20(including%20the%20TMC)%20seven.%20Effectively%2C%20the%20NDA%20won%2039%20seats%2C%20the%20INDIA%20bloc%20constituents%20eight%2C%20and%20non-aligned%20parties%20-%20namely%2C%20the%20BJD%2C%20even%20though%20it%20has%20usually%20taken%20a%20pro-BJP%20stance%20over%20the%20last%20decade%20-%20won%20two%20seats.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Flok-sabha-elections-why-a-2004-like-scenario-is-unlikely-5684511%5C%22%3ERead%20%7C%C2%A0Opinion%3A%20Why%20A%202004-Like%20Scenario%20Is%20Unlikely%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20NDA%20recorded%20an%20average%20vote%20share%20of%2053%25%20in%20the%20constituencies%20it%20won%2C%20the%20INDIA%20bloc%20constituents%20got%2050%25%2C%20while%20non-aligned%20parties%20netted%2049%25%20votes.%20In%20terms%20of%20margins%2C%20the%20BJP%20won%2012%20seats%20with%20a%20lead%20of%2010%20percentage%20points%20(pp)%20in%20terms%20of%20vote%20share%2C%20which%20can%20be%20considered%20a%20close%20contest.%20In%2020%20seats%2C%20the%20BJP%20won%20with%20a%20comfortable%20majority%20of%20more%20than%2010%25.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP%20had%20a%20strike%20rate%20of%2080%25%20for%20these%2049%20seats%2C%20even%20though%20its%20overall%20strike%20rate%20was%20lower%20at%2069%25.%20The%20Congress's%20success%20rate%2C%20in%20contrast%2C%20was%20just%203%25%20for%20these%20seats%2C%20though%20its%20all-India%20average%20was%2012%25.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20terms%20of%20turnout%2C%20this%20phase%20also%20witnessed%20a%20comparatively%20lower%20turnout%20in%202019.%20On%20the%2030%20seats%20where%20polling%20increased%2C%20the%20incumbent%20party%20lost.%20And%20in%20the%2019%20seats%20where%20the%20turnout%20decreased%20in%202019%2C%20the%20winning%20party%20from%202014%20lost%20in%20six.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EA%20Battle%20Over%20Legacy%20In%20Maharashtra%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOf%20the%2013%20seats%20in%20Maharashtra%2C%2010%20are%20in%20the%20Mumbai-Thane%20region%2C%20the%20stronghold%20of%20Shiv%20Sena.%20Here%2C%20the%20fight%20between%20Shinde%20and%20Uddhav%20factions%20will%20be%20over%20the%20legacy%20of%20Balasaheb%20Thackeray.%20Uddhav's%20estranged%20cousin%20and%20the%20leader%20of%20the%20Maharashtra%20Navnirman%20Sena%20(MNS)%2C%20Raj%20Thackeray%2C%20has%20also%20provided%20support%20to%20the%20BJP.%20The%20BJP-Shiv%20Sena%20alliance%20had%20won%20all%20of%20these%2010%20seats%20with%20a%20huge%20victory%20margin%20of%20around%2025%25%20in%20both%202014%20and%202019.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFrom%20the%20NDA%2C%20the%20BJP%20and%20the%20Shinde-led%20Shiv%20Sena%20are%20contesting%20five%20seats%20each%2C%20while%20from%20the%20INDIA%20bloc%2C%20the%20Uddhav-led%20Shiv%20Sena%20is%20contesting%20seven%2C%20the%20Congress%20two%2C%20and%20the%20Sharad%20Pawar-led%20NCP%20one.%20The%20latter%20doesn't%20have%20a%20significant%20base%20in%20the%20region.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fwhy-maharashtras-verdict-will-be-unpredictable-ndtvs-battleground-5264312%5C%22%3ERead%20%7C%C2%A0Why%20Maharashtra's%20Verdict%20Will%20Be%20Unpredictable%3A%20NDTV's%20Battleground%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20five%20seats%20-%20Kalyan%2C%20Thane%2C%20Mumbai%20North%20West%2C%20Mumbai%20South%20and%20Mumbai%20South%20Central%20-%20both%20Sena%20factions%20are%20pitted%20against%20each%20other.%20In%20total%2C%20of%20the%2013%20seats%20in%20Maharashtra%2C%20the%20Sena%20had%20won%20seven%20in%202019.%20But%20as%20many%20as%20five%20MPs%20have%20since%20shifted%20to%20the%20Shinde%20camp.%20The%20INDIA%20bloc%20hopes%20that%20Uddhav%20will%20get%20sympathy%20for%20the%20way%20his%20party%20was%20split%20by%20Shinde.%20All%20eyes%20will%20be%20on%20the%20turnout%20in%20the%20urban%20centres%2C%20which%20has%20traditionally%20been%20low.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EA%20Close%20Fight%20In%20Odisha%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20Western%20Odisha%2C%20of%20the%20five%20seats%20that%20will%20see%20polling%20on%20May%2020%2C%20the%20BJP%20had%20won%20three%20in%202019%2C%20while%20the%20BJD%20won%20two.%20The%20electoral%20fight%20appears%20to%20be%20tighter%20this%20time.%20There%20has%20also%20been%20some%20pre-poll%20violence%20in%20the%20Odisha%20Chief%20Minister's%20home%20district%2C%20Ganjam.%20One%20BJP%20supporter%20lost%20his%20life%20in%20the%20clash.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGiven%20that%20Odisha%20is%20seeing%20simultaneous%20polls%2C%20party%20strategists%20believe%20that%20an%20improved%20performance%20in%20the%20assembly%20polls%20will%20automatically%20jack%20up%20its%20numbers%20in%20the%20Lok%20Sabha.%20V.K.%20Pandian's%20elevation%20in%20the%20BJD%20has%20not%20gone%20down%20well%20with%20many%20party%20workers%20and%20leaders%2C%20and%20the%20BJP%2C%20by%20deploying%20senior%20ministers%20and%20chief%20ministers%20in%20the%20state%20campaign%2C%20hopes%20to%20capitalise%20on%20this%20sentiment.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EAdvantage%20BJP%20In%20Uttar%20Pradesh%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20Uttar%20Pradesh%2C%20the%20battle%20moves%20to%2014%20seats%20in%20the%20central%20and%20eastern%20parts%20of%20the%20state.%20State%20capital%20Lucknow%2C%20Faizabad%20(Ayodhya)%20and%20Gandhi%20family%20bastions%20Amethi%20and%20Raebareli%20are%20part%20of%20the%20battle.%20The%20BJP%20had%20swept%20this%20region%20in%20the%20last%20election%2C%20bagging%2013%20of%20the%2014%20seats%2C%20with%20Congress%20winning%20just%20Raebareli.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20time%2C%20while%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20is%20contesting%20from%20Raebareli%2C%20K.L.%20Sharma%2C%20considered%20close%20to%20the%20Gandhi%20family%2C%20is%20fighting%20from%20Amethi.%20Priyanka%20has%20been%20camping%20on%20these%20two%20seats%20for%20days%20now%20as%20it's%20a%20prestige%20battle%20for%20the%20Gandhi%20family.%20The%20SP%2C%20meanwhile%2C%20has%20changed%20its%20strategy%20and%20fielded%20more%20OBC%20candidates%20than%20the%20BJP%20in%20the%20state%20to%20breach%20the%20latter's%20fort.%20It%20has%20also%20put%20up%20fewer%20Muslim-Yadav%20candidates%20to%20shed%20its%20traditional%20image.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHow%20well%20the%20BSP%20performs%20and%20which%20party%20it%20damages%20could%20well%20determine%20whether%20the%20INDIA%20bloc%20can%20dent%20the%20BJP's%20tally%20in%20seats%20that%20are%20in%20and%20around%20Ayodhya%2C%20the%20epicentre%20of%20the%20Ram%20Mandir%20movement.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3ETriangular%20Contest%20Looming%20In%20Bengal%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20West%20Bengal%2C%20seven%20seats%20from%20the%20south%20and%20presidency%20regions%20will%20be%20voting%20in%20this%20phase.%20The%20BJP%20had%20won%20three%20seats%20in%202019%2C%20and%20the%20rest%20went%20to%20the%20TMC.%20A%20close%20battle%20is%20on%20the%20cards%20here%20as%20the%20Congress%20and%20the%20Communist%20Party%20of%20India%20(Marxist)%20(CPI-M)-led%20alliance%20are%20attempting%20to%20turn%20it%20into%20a%20triangular%20contest.%20Mamata's%20flip-flop%20on%20whether%20she%20is%20part%20of%20the%20INDIA%20bloc%20may%20also%20have%20caused%20some%20confusion%20among%20voters.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20five%20of%20the%20seven%20seats%2C%20the%20parties%20that%20ranked%20third%20in%202019%20secured%20more%20votes%20than%20the%20victory%20margin.%20So%20they%20may%20spoil%20the%20chances%20of%20either%20of%20the%20main%20contenders.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20Bihar%2C%20voting%20will%20be%20held%20in%20five%20seats%20in%20the%20north%2C%20all%20of%20which%20were%20won%20by%20the%20NDA%20in%202019%20with%20huge%20margins.%20From%20the%20NDA%2C%20the%20BJP%20is%20contesting%20three%20seats%2C%20while%20the%20Janata%20Dal%20(United)%20(JD-U)%20and%20the%20Lok%20Janshakti%20Party%20(LJP)%20are%20contesting%20one%20seat%20each.%20The%20Rashtriya%20Janata%20Dal%20(RJD)%20hopes%20to%20turn%20the%20tables%20based%20on%20its%20performance%20in%20the%202020%20assembly%20elections%2C%20the%20drop%20in%20Nitish%20Kumar's%20popularity%20due%20to%20his%20flip-flops.%20He%20is%20also%20banking%20on%20the%20boost%20his%20own%20image%20received%20for%20generating%20jobs%20as%20deputy%20chief%20minister.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(Amitabh%20Tiwari%20is%20a%20political%20strategist%20and%20commentator.%20In%20his%20earlier%20avatar%2C%20he%20was%20a%20corporate%20and%20investment%20banker.)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDisclaimer%3A%20These%20are%20the%20personal%20opinions%20of%20the%20author.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1716090900000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.ndtvimg.com%2Fi%2F2015-09%2F