al%20Court%20for%20the%20trial%20of%20former%20US%20President%20Donald%20Trump%20charged%20with%20covering%20up%20hush%20money%20payments%20linked%20to%20extramarital%20affairs%2C%20in%20New%20York%20City%2C%20on%20May%2016%2C%202024.%20Trump's%20defense%20team%20Thursday%20continues%20the%20questioning%20of%20Michael%20Cohen%2C%20the%20key%20witness%20in%20the%20criminal%20trial%20of%20the%20former%20president.%20(Photo%20by%20ANGELA%20WEISS%20%2F%20AFP)%20(Photo%20by%20ANGELA%20WEISS%2FAFP%20via%20Getty%20Images)%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6648c35a20abc1efe8fb5fbc%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22683%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EMembers%20of%20the%20public%20line%20up%20to%20get%20inside%20the%20Manhattan%20court%20to%20watch%20Donald%20Trump's%20hush-money%20trial.%3Cp%3EANGELA%20WEISS%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20high%20demand%20for%20spots%20has%20also%20been%20leading%20to%20big%20money%20offers%20for%20places%20toward%20the%20front%20of%20the%20queue.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20Thursday%20morning%2C%20one%20woman%20who%20was%2012th%20in%20line%20was%20offering%20her%20place%20for%20%24450%2C%20while%20a%20lawyer%20behind%20had%20shelled%20out%20hundreds%20of%20dollars%20for%20line%20sitters%20so%20she%20could%20get%20a%20place%20in%20an%20overflow%20room%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nytimes.com%2F2024%2F05%2F16%2Fnyregion%2Ftrump-trial-line-overflow.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EThe%20New%20York%20Times%3C%2Fa%3E%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20first%20person%20in%20line%20on%20Wednesday%20morning%20had%20paid%20%241%2C800%20for%20someone%20to%20keep%20their%20spot%20for%20them%2C%20the%20NBC%20News%20report%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESince%20the%20trial%20began%2C%20Samuels%20said%20he%20had%20doubled%20his%20prices%20from%20%2425%20to%20%2450%20per%20hour%20and%20increased%20the%20number%20of%20line%20standers%20he%20has%20available%20from%2026%20to%2032%2C%20the%20report%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2293c03103-c7b1-47b7-922e-8df13b19168d%5C%22%3ELine%20sitting%20is%20a%20controversial%20practice%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EProfessional%20line%20sitters%20help%20people%20wait%20for%20hugely%20popular%20events%20or%20offerings%2C%20such%20as%20buying%20the%20latest%20sneakers%20or%20seats%20at%20exclusive%20restaurants.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhether%20it's%20iPhones%2C%20the%20latest%20Air%20Jordans%2C%20or%20the%20hottest%20Broadway%20tix%20in%20town%2C%20Same%20Ole%20Line%20Dudes%2C%20understands%20your%20wants%20%26amp%3B%20needs%20and%20is%20here%20to%20help%2C%26quot%3B%20Same%20Ole%20Line%20Dudes%20says%20on%20its%20website.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20high-profile%20trials%20are%20often%20the%20big%20moneymakers%20for%20such%20firms.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20Washington-based%20professional%20line%20stander%20previously%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fprofessional-line-stander-skip-the-line-cost-how-it-works-2022-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etold%20BI%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20was%20one%20of%20her%20biggest%20money-spinners.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BFor%20Supreme%20Court%20lines%20we%20charged%20%2440%20an%20hour%20per%20person.%20That%20was%20the%20most%20expensive%20line%20because%20it%20was%20a%20limited-seating%20event%20and%20a%20longer%20wait%2C%20and%20we%20had%20to%20plan%20more%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20her%20usual%20rate%20was%20%2425%20to%20%2435%20an%20hour.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20longest%20we%20have%20camped%20out%20in%20a%20line%20was%20for%20a%20Supreme%20Court%20case%2C%20for%20three%20to%20four%20days.%20For%20these%20kinds%20of%20lines%20we%20have%20a%20group%20of%20people%20who%20rotate%20so%20that%20everyone%20gets%20to%20take%20a%20break%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20continued.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20professional%20line%20standing%20has%20been%20a%20controversial%20practice%2C%20especially%20for%20courtroom%20spaces.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Supreme%20Court%20says%20on%20its%20website%20that%20attorneys%20who%20are%20admitted%20as%20members%20of%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20Bar%20must%20not%20employ%20line%20sitters%20to%20hold%20their%20places%20to%20hear%20arguments.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOnly%20Bar%20members%20who%20actually%20intend%20to%20attend%20argument%20are%20allowed%20in%20line%20for%20the%20Bar%20section%3B%20'line%20standers'%20are%20not%20permitted%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMembers%20of%20the%20public%20do%20not%20face%20the%20same%20restrictions%2C%20however.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fline-sitters-cash-in-on-donald-trump-hush-money-trial-2024-5%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1716053967000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6648c2eb14fb5b23cc5e110c%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fline-sitters-cash-in-on-donald-trump-hush-money-trial-2024-5%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20first%20person%20in%20line%20for%20Trump's%20Manhattan%20trial%20on%20Wednesday%20morning%20paid%20%241%2C800%20for%20someone%20to%20keep%20their%20spot%2C%20NBC%20News%20reported.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22cmanley%40businessinsider.com%20(Cameron%20Manley)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A27%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fline-sitters-cash-in-on-donald-trump-hush-money-trial-2024-5%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Thousands%20flock%20to%20see%20former%20South%20African%20president%20as%20he%20turns%20against%20former%20party%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1716053580000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fe3.365dm.com%2F24%2F05%2F1920x1080%2Fskynews-zuma-south-africa_6558676.jpg%3F20240518185611%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Fsouth-africa-elections-former-president-jac