ers-trek-route%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20Valley%20of%20Flowers%E2%80%9D%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%20published%20in%201937.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAptly%20put%20by%20an%3Cem%3E%20Inside%20Himalayas%3C%2Fem%3E%20article%2C%20%E2%80%9CYou%20don%E2%80%99t%20quite%20understand%20how%20lucky%20you%20are%20until%20you%20get%20there.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhatever%20you%20might%20have%20heard%2C%20whatever%20photographs%20you%20might%20have%20seen%2C%20absolutely%20nothing%20prepares%20you%20for%20that%20burst%20of%20colour%20as%20far%20as%20the%20eyes%20can%20see%2C%20framed%20by%20mist-shrouded%2C%20snow-powdered%20mountain%20ranges%20whose%20tops%20disappear%20into%20the%20sky.%20You%20feel%20as%20though%20you%20have%20arrived%20at%20the%20top%20of%20the%20world%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20article%20elaborates.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2Fvalley-of-flowers-1-1715929674.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20valley%20of%20flowers%20was%20declared%20a%20UNESCO%20World%20Heritage%20Site%20in%202005%2C%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2Fvalley-of-flowers-1-1715929674.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2Fvalley-of-flowers-1-1715929674-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2Fvalley-of-flowers-1-1715929674-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2Fvalley-of-flowers-1-1715929674-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2Fvalley-of-flowers-1-1715929674-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-350347%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EThe%20valley%20of%20flowers%20was%20declared%20a%20UNESCO%20World%20Heritage%20Site%20in%202005%2C%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENestled%20in%20the%20Chamoli%20District%20of%20Uttarakhand%2C%20the%20place%20comes%20alive%20in%20the%20monsoon%20months%20blossoming%20with%20flowers%20of%20more%20than%20500%20varieties%20including%20the%20Himalayan%20Slipper%20Orchid%2C%20Brahma%20Kamal%2C%20Marsh%20Marigold%2C%20Blue%20Poppy%2C%20Cobra%20Lily%2C%20and%20Himalayan%20native%20Dactylorhiza%20Hatagirea.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EApart%20from%20the%20natural%20allure%2C%20the%20place%20is%20also%20said%20to%20have%20religious%20significance.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20a%20%3Cem%3ELifestyle%20Asia%20report%2C%20%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20national%20park%20also%20holds%20a%20significant%20mythological%20association.%20According%20to%20the%20epic%20Ramayana%2C%20it%20is%20the%20place%20where%20Lord%20Hanuman%20found%20the%20magical%20herb%20%E2%80%9CSanjeevani%E2%80%9D%20to%20help%20save%20Lakshman%2C%20brother%20of%20Lord%20Rama%2C%20who%20was%20injured%20during%20the%20battle%20between%20Lord%20Rama%20and%20demon%20King%20Ravana.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EHow%20to%20reach%20the%20valley%3F%C2%A0%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20planning%20a%20trek%20to%20the%20Valley%20of%20Flowers%20in%20Uttarakhand%2C%20it%E2%80%99s%20important%20to%20consider%20the%20most%20convenient%20modes%20of%20transportation%20to%20reach%20your%20starting%20point%20at%20Govindghat.%20Here%E2%80%99s%20how%20you%20can%20get%20there%20%E2%80%93%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EBy%20Car%3A%20%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EYou%20can%20drive%20from%20major%20cities%20like%20Delhi%20or%20Dehradun%20to%20Govindghat.%20The%20journey%20from%20Delhi%20takes%20approximately%2010-12%20hours%2C%20depending%20on%20traffic%20and%20road%20conditions.%20From%20Delhi%2C%20you%20can%20also%20avail%20public%20transport%20from%20ISBT%20or%20Delhi%20Gate%20to%20Rishikesh%20and%20take%20another%20bus%20to%20Joshimath%20and%20then%20to%20Govindghat.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EYou%E2%80%99ll%20travel%20through%20major%20towns%20such%20as%20Rishikesh%20and%20Haridwar%20before%20reaching%20Govindghat.%20The%20roads%20are%20scenic%2C%20offering%20beautiful%20views%20of%20the%20mountains%20and%20rivers%20along%20the%20way.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EBy%20Air%3A%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20nearest%20airport%20to%20Govindghat%20is%20Jolly%20Grant%20Airport%20in%20Dehradun.%20From%20the%20airport%2C%20you%20can%20hire%20a%20taxi%20or%20take%20a%20bus%20to%20Govindghat.%20The%20drive%20from%20Dehradun%20to%20Govindghat%20is%20286%20km%20and%20takes%20approximately%2010-12%20hours%2C%20so%20you%20might%20want%20to%20plan%20your%20flight%20arrival%20time%20accordingly.%3Cbr%3E%3Cbr%3EYou%20can%20opt%20for%20public%20transport%20from%20Dehradun%20to%20Rishikesh%20and%20then%20to%20Joshimath%20and%20so%20on.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20data-instgrm-captioned%20data-instgrm-version%3D%5C%2214%5C%22%20data-instgrm-permalink%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Freel%2FC6pxBHnySgj%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26amp%3Butm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Freel%2FC6pxBHnySgj%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26utm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3EView%20this%20post%20on%20Instagram%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C