20ideas%2C%20and%20every%20meeting%20between%20the%20duo%20inadvertently%20involved%20discussing%20viable%20options.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CPuru%20convinced%20us%20(my%20wife%20and%20me)%20to%20move%20to%20China%20as%20he%20felt%20that%20it%20was%20a%20great%20place%20to%20start%20a%20venture.%20We%20moved%20there%20for%20a%20year%20in%202010%20but%20realised%20that%20it%20wouldn%E2%80%99t%20be%20feasible%20to%20scale%20a%20business%20there%2C%E2%80%9D%20Sreejith%2C%20COO%20of%20True%20Elements%2C%20tells%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20he%20learnt%20an%20important%20lesson%20in%20China.%20The%20Chinese%20had%20very%20good%20food%20habits.%20%E2%80%9CThey%20cook%20food%20correctly%2C%20eat%20right%2C%20and%20most%20importantly%2C%20consume%20food%20at%20the%20right%20time.%20We%20do%20all%20three%20wrong%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20realisation%2C%20coupled%20with%20the%20health-related%20challenges%20at%20their%20house%20solidified%20the%20need%20to%20create%20a%20change%20in%20this%20sector.%20Puru%20lost%20his%20father%20to%20cancer%2C%20while%20Sreejith%E2%80%99s%20father-in-law%20died%20of%20heart%20disease.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20realised%20as%20a%20family%20that%20we%20never%20gave%20importance%20to%20preventative%20healthcare.%20We%20only%20take%20care%20of%20our%20health%20when%20it%E2%80%99s%20too%20late%2C%20or%20when%20some%20parameters%20are%20off%20the%20charts.%20Why%20do%20we%20react%20so%20late%3F%20We%20could%20have%20taken%20care%20of%20it%20earlier%2C%E2%80%9D%20shares%20Puru%2C%20CEO%20of%20True%20Elements.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20five%20years%20of%20brainstorming%2C%20Puru%20quit%20his%20job%20in%202011%20and%20started%20working%20on%20creating%20awareness%20about%20health%20and%20the%20importance%20of%20consuming%20the%20right%20food.%20The%20first%20company%20that%20the%20duo%20started%20was%20called%20%E2%80%98Healthy%20World%E2%80%99%20%E2%80%94%