l%E2%80%99%20brand%20by%20the%20Clean%20Label%20Project%2C%20US%2C%20and%20100%20percent%20whole%20grain%20brand%20by%20the%20Whole%20Grains%20Council%2C%20US.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20a%20presence%20built%20around%20300%20towns%20in%20India%20with%20over%20300%20employees%2C%20supplying%20to%20over%20five%20lakh%20households%20every%20month%2C%20the%20duo%20are%20working%20towards%20their%20mission%20of%20providing%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F340611%2Fhealthy-snack-brand-startup-open-secret-woman-entrepreneur-ahana-gautam-iit-bombay-harvard%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehealthy%20food%20options%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20Indians.%20They%20are%20clear%20on%20their%20solution%20%E2%80%94%20clean%20food%20%E2%80%94%20the%20reason%20they%20stay%20away%20from%20products%20like%20protein%20supplements.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhat%E2%80%99s%20their%20message%20to%20budding%20entrepreneurs%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-quote%20wp-block-quote-is-layout-flow%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%E2%80%9CDon%E2%80%99t%20overthink%2C%20just%20start%20up.%20There%20will%20never%20be%20a%20perfect%20time.%20Dive%20in%20with%20a%20childlike%20mindset%2C%20and%20just%20like%20children%20do%20when%20they%20fall%20down%2C%20stand%20up%20and%20try%20again.%20It%E2%80%99s%20okay%20to%20fall%20down%20and%20fail.%20Shun%20the%20need%20for%20validation%20and%20fear%20of%20judgement%2C%E2%80%9D%20shares%20Puru.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20all%20the%20youngsters%20who%20believe%20that%20you%20can%20succeed%20in%20a%20year%2C%20Sreejith%20has%20some%20words%20of%20wisdom.%20%E2%80%9CNo%20one%20arrives%20in%20a%20year%2C%20it%20takes%20at%20least%20six%20years.%20Don%E2%80%99t%20give%20up%20before%20these%20six%20to%20seven%20years%20and%20don%E2%80%99t%20be%20afraid%20of%20going%20down%20to%20zero%2C%E2%80%9D%20shares%20Sreejith.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Pranita%20Bhat%2C%20Images%20Courtesy%20True%20Elements%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1715929549000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2FCover-image-15-1715860333.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D350165%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Sreejith%20Moolayil%20and%20Puru%20Gupta%20overcame%20challenges%20to%20build%20their%20healthy%20food%20brand%2C%20True%20Elements.%20Despite%20early%20failures%20and%20financial%20struggles%2C%20their%20commitment%20to%20preventative%20healthcare%20and%20transparency%20led%20to%20a%20multi-crore%20business.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Sowmya%20Mani%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F350165%2Fpuru-gupta-sreejith-moolayil-true-elements-pune-marico-healthy-snacks-rolled-oats-muesli-chia-seeds%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Why%20an%2087-YO%20Trained%201%20Lakh%20Indians%20On%20How%20to%20Save%20Lives%20After%20Road%20Accidents%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EReflecting%20on%20when%20she%20received%20the%20Padma%20Shri%20award%20for%20her%20contributions%20to%20road%20safety%20in%20India%2C%20Dr%20Maya%20Tandon%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CIt%20was%20the%20greatest%20moment%20of%20my%20life.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%2087-year-old%20retired%20anesthesiologist%20has%20devoted%20her%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F142778%2Fassam-dgp-cop-maths-teacher-govt-school%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20post-retirement%20years%20%3C%2Fa%3Eto%20making%20Indian%20roads%20safer.%20%E2%80%9CWhile%20many%20are%20familiar%20with%20road%20safety%20protocols%20and%20first%20aid%2C%20few%20know%20how%20to%20perform%20them%20effectively%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20said%20in%20a%20conversation%20with%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDr%20Maya%20trains%20people%20in%20road%20safety%20through%20her%20organisation%20%E2%80%98Sahayta%20Trust%E2%80%99.%20Working%20relentlessly%20for%20the%20past%20three%20decades%2C%20she%20says%20she%20has%20trained%201%2C33%2C000%20people%20in%20road%20safety%2C%20CRP%20(cardiopulmonary%20resuscitation)%2C%20sequential%20handling%2C%20and%20protocol%20dealings%20with%20accidents.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20a%20zeal%20for%20life%20and%20a%20passion%20for%20working%20for%20society%20%E2%80%94%20stronger%20than%20ever%20%E2%80%94%20Dr%20Maya%20reflects%20on%20her%20journey%20and%20shares%20what%20led%20her%20to%20this%20path.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EWhen%20saving%20lives%20became%20her%20mission%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBorn%20and%20raised%20in%20Ajmer%2C%20Dr%20Maya%20was%20a%20starry-eyed%20child%20who%20dreamt%20of%20doing%20something%20great.%20%E2%80%9CGiven%20the%20times%20that%20I%20was%20born%20in%2C%20my%20family%20was%20very%20supportive%20and%20liberal.%20I%20scored%20good%20marks%20on%20the%20school%20board%20exams%20and%20got%20admitted%20to%20medical%20school%20in%20Ajmer%20and%20Delhi%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20recalls.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20grew%20up%20in%20luxury%2C%20which%20allowed%20her%20the%20freedom%20to%20choose%20her%20own%20path%20in%20life.%20So%20she%20decided%20to%20pursue%20a%20career%20in%20medical%20science.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20did%20my%20internship%20in%20Ajmer%2C%20where%20I%20met%20my%20husband.%20We%20decided%20to%20get%20married%20and%20moved%20to%20Jaipur%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20recalls.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%201968%2C%20Dr%20Maya%20gave%20birth%20to%20her%20son.%20%E2%80%9CAfter%20that%2C%20I%20chose%20to%20pursue%20a%20diploma%20in%20anesthesiology%20because%20it%20was%20a%20career%20that%20I%20could%20manage%20while%20raising%20a%20family.%20By%20the%20time%20I%20completed%20my%20diploma%2C%20I%20had%20also%20given%20birth%20to%20another%20child%2C%20my%20daughter%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%201972%2C%20she%20also%20did%20an%20MS%20in%20anaesthesia.%20%E2%80%9CI%20was%20also%20giving%20lectures%20on%20anaesthesia%20at%20a%20medical%20college%20in%20Jaipur%20where%20I%20came%20across%20an%20opportunity.%20It%20was%20a%20fellowship%20in%20London%20for%20paediatric%20anaesthesia.%20With%20my%20family%E2%80%99s%20support%2C%20I%20was%20able%20to%20attend%20that%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2Favocado-6-1715867697.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2Favocado-6-1715867697.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2Favocado-6-1715867697-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2Favocado-6-1715867697-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2Favocado-6-1715867697-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2Favocado-6-1715867697-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-350314%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EDr%20Maya%20Tandon%2C%20a%20Padma%20Shri%20Awardee.%20%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20completing%20her%20fellowship%2C%20she%20returned%20to%20India%20and%20began%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F251637%2Frajasthan-startup-newndra-innovation-ganesh-ram-jangir-jaipur-belt-back-pain-farmer-help-make-in-india-ros174%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eworking%20in%20Jaipur.%20%E2%80%9C%3C%2Fa%3EThe%20role%20of%20an%20anesthesiologist%20is%20often%20seen%20as%20a%20behind-the-curtain%20job.%20However%2C%20for%20me%20and%20in%20medical%20sciences%2C%20the%20patient%E2%80%99s%20life%20depends%20on%20us%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20emphasises%2C%20highlighting%20her%20deep%20interest%20in%20lifesaving%20work.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%201975%2C%20she%20earned%20the%20honour%20of%20becoming%20superintendent%20and%20spent%20the%20rest%20of%20her%20career%20managing%20the%20hospital%20while%20serving%20as%20the%20head%20of%20anaesthesia%20at%20Sawai%20Man%20Singh%20Hospital.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIt%20was%20around%20the%20time%20of%20my%20retirement%20in%201985%20when%20the%20Rajasthan%20Police%20Academy%20in%20Jaipur%20contacted%20me%20and%20requested%20I%20give%20a%20three-day%20course%20on%20road%20safety%20and%20lifesaving.%20I%20readily%20agreed%20to%20the%20request%2C%20unaware%20that%20it%20would%20shape%20the%20course%20of%20my%20post-retirement%20life%2C%E2%80%9D%20Dr%20Maya%20reminisces.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20course%20was%20very%20successful%20and%20all%20the%20senior%20officers%20posted%20on%20highways%20in%20and%20around%20Jaipur%20were%20sent%20to%20her%20for%20yet%20another%20course.%20%E2%80%9CA%20photographer%20had%20come%20to%20take%20some%20pictures%20of%20the%20event.%20It%20was%20a%20few%20months%20later%20that%20he%20rang%20me%20up%20and%20told%20me%20that%20I%20had%20saved%20his%20life%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20shares.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20photographer%20had%20been%20in%20an%20accident%20and%20could%20feel%20bleeding%20in%20his%20inner%20thighs%20and%20back.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20people%20around%20him%20were%20not%20sure%20how%20to%20help%20him%20and%20were%20taking%20pictures%20of%20him.%20He%20explained%20someone%20to%20lift%20him%20and%20put%20him%20in%20a%20certain%20position%20that%20slowed%20the%20bleeding%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20narrates.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20timely%20move%20reduced%20the%20blood%20loss%20and%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F317185%2Fbollywood-celebrity-photographer-munna-thaakur-recalls-struggle-story%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esaved%20the%20photographer%E2%80%99s%20life.%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%9CHis%20words%20and%20appreciation%20made%20me%20realise%20the%20importance%20of%20offering%20such%20courses.%20It%20also%20revealed%20the%20sad%20reality%20of%20the%20state%20of%20road%20safety%20in%20India.%20Not%20one%20of%20the%20persons%20in%20the%20crowd%20knew%20lifesaving%20steps%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20an%20intention%20to%20change%20the%20scenario%20of%20road%20safety%20in%20India%2C%20Dr%20Maya%20started%20the%20Sahayta%20Trust.%20Since%20then%2C%20she%20has%20given%20free%20courses%2C%20seminars%2C%20and%20lectures%20to%20over%201%2C33%2C000%20individuals.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAll%20these%20courses%20are%20conducted%20free%20of%20charge.%20The%20aim%20is%20to%20raise%20awareness%20about%20CPR%20(cardiopulmonary%20resuscitation)%2C%20proper%20handling%20techniques%2C%20and%20protocols%20for%20dealing%20with%20accidents.%20We%20also%20inform%20participants%20about%20the%20various%20laws%20that%20protect%20a%20lifesaver%20from%20police%20investigation%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20explains.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2Favocado-7-1715867783.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2Favocado-7-1715867783.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2Favocado-7-1715867783-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2Favocado-7-1715867783-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2Favocado-7-1715867783-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2Favocado-7-1715867783-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-350315%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnil%20Kumar%20Gill%20from%20Gudha%20Godji%2C%20a%20small%20town%20in%20Rajasthan%2C%20participated%20in%20the%20seminar%20on%20road%20safety.%20%E2%80%9CI%20was%20going%20about%20my%20day%2C%20working%20in%20my%20shop%2C%20when%20I%20got%20to%20know%20that%20a%20team%20from%20Jaipur%20had%20reached%20our%20small%20town.%20I%20was%20keen%20to%20know%20what%20they%20were%20sharing%20and%20had%20to%20try%20it.%20We%20are%20always%20aware%20of%20the%20safety%20threats%20on%20the%20road%20but%20attending%20the%20seminar%20helped%20me%20understand%20what%20can%20be%20done%20to%20save%20a%20life%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20were%20told%20how%20we%20can%20give%20CPR%20and%20first%20aid%20to%20an%20injured%20person.%20We%20were%20also%20given%20instructions%20about%20who%20we%20can%20contact%20for%20help%20if%20a%20person%20needs%20to%20be%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F338010%2Fkerala-startup-mykare-building-uber-of-healthcare-for-surgeries%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20taken%20to%20the%20hospital.%20%3C%2Fa%3EThey%20also%20told%20us%20about%20the%20various%20road%20safety%20rules%20and%20laws%2C%20which%20I%20had%20no%20idea%20existed.%20I%20think%20such%20seminars%20are%20very%20important%20as%20there%20is%20a%20lack%20of%20awareness%20in%20rural%20areas%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EHow%20you%20can%20help%3F%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETalking%20about%20how%20there%20is%20a%20lack%20of%20awareness%20among%20bystanders%20during%20an%20accident%2C%20she%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CPeople%20have%20a%20misconception%20about%20helping%20a%20person%20who%20has%20had%20an%20accident.%20There%20are%20clear%20laws%20that%20save%20the%20bystanders%20from%20any%20kind%20of%20investigation%2C%20but%20there%20are%20not%20many%20people%20who%20know%20this.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPointing%20out%20that%20this%20lack%20of%20awareness%20brings%20hesitation%20in%20people%20to%20help%20the%20injured%20person%2C%20she%20adds%2C%20%E2%80%9CEven%20if%20you%20can%E2%80%99t%20give%20mouth%20to%20mouth%20to%20a%20person%20who%20has%20collapsed%2C%20say%20due%20to%20heart%20attack%2C%20giving%20CPR%20can%20save%20their%20life.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EExplaining%20what%20levels%20of%20intervention%20Sahayta%20Trust%20does%2C%20Dr%20Maya%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CWe%20have%20different%20ways%20of%20reaching%20out%20to%20the%20public.%20We%20do%20seminars%20both%20online%20and%20offline%3B%20we%20also%20conduct%20workshops%20and%20classes.%20Additionally%2C%20we%20also%20do%20rallies%20and%20street%20plays%20to%20raise%20awareness.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20module%20that%20the%20trust%20follows%20for%20the%20seminars%20and%20courses%20is%20Maya%E2%80%99s%20speciality.%20%E2%80%9CIn%20a%20small%20course%2C%20we%20prioritise%20giving%20them%20the%20instructions%20of%20what%20to%20do%20in%20the%20first%2010%20seconds%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20informs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CCheck%20for%20head%20injuries%20and%20bleeding%3B%20once%20you%20have%20secured%20what%20the%20problem%20is%2C%20you%20can%20act%20accordingly.%20If%20a%20person%E2%80%99s%20lungs%20and%20heart%20are%20giving%20out%2C%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F191316%2Fias-hero-inspiring-civil-servants-save-lives-daman-collector-india%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eresorting%20to%20CPR%20is%20the%20best%20way.%3C%2Fa%3E%20Time%20is%20of%20the%20essence%20when%20there%20is%20internal%20bleeding.%20If%20a%20person%20is%20suffering%20from%20cardiac%20arrest%2C%20only%20an%20external%20CPR%20can%20help%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EApart%20from%20courses%20and%20training%2C%20the%20trust%20also%20works%20with%20government%20agencies%20to%20ensure%20that%20there%20are%20emergency%20services%20in%20public%20places%20like%20malls%20and%20airports.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20major%20hurdle%20that%20Maya%20faces%20is%20to%20bring%20people%20to%20attend%20the%20workshops.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20Indian%20public%20is%20always%20in%20a%20hurry.%20It%20is%20very%20hard%20for%20them%20to%20take%20time%20and%20reach%20us.%20We%20see%20a%20low%20rate%20of%20response%20as%20they%20don%E2%80%99t%20have%20time%20to%20keep%20visiting%20our%20courses%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIndia%20is%20leading%20in%20road%20accidents%20and%20road%20deaths.%20To%20combat%20this%20lack%20of%20response%2C%20we%20are%20working%20on%20a%20model%20where%20we%20train%20people%2C%20especially%20from%20rural%20areas%2C%20in%20lifesaving.%20And%20then%20they%20reach%20out%20to%20more%2C%E2%80%9D%20Dr%20Maya%20informs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2Favocado-8-1715867846.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Dr%20Maya%20has%20trained%20over%201%20lakh%20people%20in%20life%20saving%20and%20road%20safety.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2Favocado-8-1715867846.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2Favocado-8-1715867846-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2Favocado-8-1715867846-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2Favocado-8-1715867846-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2Favocado-8-1715867846-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-350316%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20c