ndia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2FPirul-1715763820-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-350008%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3ENupur%20(left)%20and%20her%20sister%20Sharvari%20started%20%E2%80%98PIRUL%20Handicrafts%E2%80%99%20to%20make%20artefacts%20from%20pine%20needles.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECurrently%2C%20the%20team%20manufactures%20various%20handicraft%20products%20like%20tea%20coasters%2C%20earrings%2C%20storage%20boxes%2C%20handbags%2C%20serving%20trays%2C%20table%20mats%2C%20and%20planters.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EStarting%20with%2015%20women%20initially%2C%20the%20team%20has%20expanded%20to%20100%20women%20from%20seven%20villages%20like%20KhetiKhan%2C%20Tyarsun%2C%20Patan%2C%20Chaanmari%2C%20Panda%2C%20Paati%2C%20and%20Jhulaghat.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESunita%20Moni%2C%20who%20has%20been%20working%20with%20the%20startup%20for%20the%20past%20three%20years%2C%20tells%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E%2C%20%E2%80%9CEarlier%2C%20I%20used%20to%20rear%20livestock%20and%20grow%20wheat%20and%20paddy%20on%20two%20%3Cem%3Ebigha%20%3C%2Fem%3Eof%20our%20land.%20Often%2C%20we%20would%20incur%20huge%20losses%20because%20of%20forest%20fires%20that%20would%20burn%20down%20our%20crops%2C%20fodder%20for%20our%20cows%2C%20even%20houses%2C%20and%20dry%20water%20resources.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20didn%E2%80%99t%20know%20that%20pine%20waste%20can%20be%20turned%20into%20beautiful%20craft%20items.%20It%20is%20exciting%20to%20make%20new%20designs%20every%20day.%20With%20this%2C%20my%20monthly%20income%20has%20also%20increased%20from%20Rs%201%2C500%20to%20Rs%205%2C000.%20As%20a%20result%2C%20I%20was%20able%20to%20enrol%20both%20of%20my%20kids%20in%20private%20schools.%20Over%20these%20years%2C%20I%20also%20saved%20some%20of%20this%20amount%20to%20buy%20one%20%3Cem%3Etola%20%3C%2Fem%3E(nearly%2012%20grams)%20of%20gold%20to%20secure%20the%20future%20of%20m