t%20of%20illegal%20trade%2C%20an%20issue%20that%20Chaturvedi%20is%20attempting%20to%20tackle%2C%20Picture%20source%3A%20Chaturvedi%20%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20plant%20within%20itself%20holds%20great%20possibility%20due%20to%20the%20soil%20binding%20properties%20of%20the%20root%20system%2C%20a%20characteristic%20that%20could%20prove%20useful%20in%20minimising%20soil%20runoff%20from%20hill%20slopes.%20Add%20to%20this%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F73988%2Fantioxidant-rich-foods-combat-pollution-stress%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eantioxidant%20properties%3C%2Fa%3E%20possessed%20by%20the%20plant%E2%80%99s%20roots%2C%20stems%20and%20leaves%2C%20and%20it%20is%20a%20golden%20foliage.%20%E2%80%9CCurrently%2C%20there%20are%20800%20Patwa%20plants%20that%20are%20thriving%2C%E2%80%9D%20Chaturvedi%20notes.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIllegal%20trade%20has%20been%20the%20biggest%20contributing%20factor%20to%20the%20slow%20death%20of%20this%20miracle%20plant.%20Highlighting%20the%20problem%2C%20Chaturvedi%20says%2C%20the%20plant%20habitats%20bordering%20Tibet%20and%20Nepal%20lead%20to%20a%20surge%20in%20cases.%20But%20even%20as%20he%20adds%20that%20cracking%20down%20on%20these%20cases%20lies%20beyond%20his%20jurisdiction%2C%20he%20is%20reminded%20of%20a%20childhood%20anecdote.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIf%20you%20want%20to%20shorten%20an%20existing%20line%2C%20just%20draw%20a%20bigger%20line%20next%20to%20it.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20this%20end%2C%20Chaturvedi%20learnt%20early%20on%20that%20the%20only%20way%20to%20ensure%20that%20the%20plant%20species%20of%20Uttarakhand%20thrived%20despite%20all%20odds%20was%20to%20ensure%20their%20propagation%20was%20amped%20up.%20%E2%80%9CSince%20day%20one%2C%20we%20have%20made%20it%20our%20motto%20that%20if%20there%20are%20100%20plants%20in%20the%20initial%20habitat%2C%20we%20will%20grow%20500%20i